962
00:32:22,140 --> 00:32:26,280
 Koja razlika je između odgoja i edukacije?

963
00:32:26,280 --> 00:32:29,740
 Kad govorimo o obrazovanju i odgoju?

964
00:32:29,740 --> 00:32:30,200
 To odgoj je prvo.

965
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:31,620
 Pa prvo.

966
00:32:31,880 --> 00:32:33,120
 Kako bi definirali jedno?

967
00:32:33,120 --> 00:32:35,240
 Pa mora dete da nauči svoje granice.

968
00:32:35,240 --> 00:32:38,420
 Mora da nauči šta je dobro, šta nije dobro.

969
00:32:38,420 --> 00:32:40,560
 Mora da nauči da se potrudi.

970
00:32:40,560 --> 00:32:41,860
 Mora da nauči da pomogne.

971
00:32:41,860 --> 00:32:43,100
 Gdje ima osjećaj za druge?

972
00:32:44,760 --> 00:32:45,940
 Odgoj je usmjeren na to.

973
00:32:45,940 --> 00:32:49,180
 Pa moram učiti dete u nekim granicama.

974
00:32:49,440 --> 00:32:50,700
 Ako mi to ne naučimo dete,

975
00:32:50,700 --> 00:32:51,540
 ko će ga naučiti?

976
00:32:51,540 --> 00:32:52,240
 Pa niko.

977
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:53,960
 Da li je to zadatak roditelja ili učitelja?

978
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:54,800
 Prvo roditelja.

979
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:55,740
 Prvo roditelja.

980
00:32:55,740 --> 00:32:57,760
 Onda vrtići škole.

981
00:32:59,620 --> 00:33:01,800
 Ali ako nama dete dođe u školu,

982
00:33:01,800 --> 00:33:04,140
 koja ne sluša nikog,

983
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:07,220
 koja traži da se njemu ispunjavaju želje,

984
00:33:07,220 --> 00:33:09,540
 neće da uči.

985
00:33:09,540 --> 00:33:12,600
 Udara drugu decu.

986
00:33:12,600 --> 00:33:14,840
 Viče na učiteljicu.

987
00:33:14,840 --> 00:33:16,700
 Kako mi njega da učimo?

988
00:33:16,700 --> 00:33:17,960
 Šta da ga učimo?

989
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:20,040
 To je već propušteno nešto.

990
00:33:20,040 --> 00:33:22,700
 A onda još gore dođu roditelji,

991
00:33:22,700 --> 00:33:24,540
 pa se svađu s učiteljima.

992
00:33:24,540 --> 00:33:27,540
 To je moje dete, to je moje blagod.

993
00:33:27,540 --> 00:33:29,100
 Ja sam imao tih situacija.

994
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:30,640
 Neću govoriti mena, ali pazite,

995
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:33,300
 imao sam mali, jedan, devet godina,

996
00:33:33,300 --> 00:33:34,500
 imamo NTC kampove.

997
00:33:34,500 --> 00:33:36,240
 Imamo, znači, Srbija, Hrvatska,

998
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:37,980
 sad smo imali u Sloveniji, Crnogori.

999
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:41,100
 I taj mali dolazi, nisam ja znao

1000
00:33:41,100 --> 00:33:42,220
 da on ima neki problem.

1001
00:33:42,220 --> 00:33:44,100
 Ali vidim da se čudno ponaša.

1002
00:33:44,100 --> 00:33:47,500
 Odjednom, on se trese

1003
00:33:47,500 --> 00:33:48,620
 i kreće da vrišti.

1004
00:33:48,620 --> 00:33:52,280
 I brzo, šta je bilo, ništa.

1005
00:33:52,280 --> 00:33:56,500
 Onda nije prošlo dugo,

1006
00:33:56,500 --> 00:33:58,180
 dva sata, krene da vrišti

1007
00:33:58,180 --> 00:33:59,140
 i uzme do sebe,

1008
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:00,820
 devočicu čupe za kosu.

1009
00:34:00,820 --> 00:34:02,280
 I brzo do njega, šta je to?

1010
00:34:02,280 --> 00:34:02,920
 Ništa.

1011
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:07,100
 Ali on je agresivan prema slabio,

1012
00:34:07,100 --> 00:34:08,260
 je djece ne prema jače.

1013
00:34:08,260 --> 00:34:09,400
 Znači, on se kontroliše.

1014
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:10,540
 Znači, da ima neki implus,

1015
00:34:10,540 --> 00:34:12,200
 bez koji mora negde da potroši.

1016
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:14,400
 Ja mu kažem,

1017
00:34:14,860 --> 00:34:16,320
 slušaj,

1018
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:17,440
 ja budem malo strok

1019
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:18,540
 na tom kampu.

1020
00:34:18,540 --> 00:34:19,900
 Ne može baš sva

1021
00:34:19,900 --> 00:34:21,340
 deca da rade šta hoće.

1022
00:34:21,340 --> 00:34:22,880
 U sve ne može niko da radi šta hoće.

1023
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:23,720
 Kažem, vidi,

1024
00:34:23,720 --> 00:34:25,920
 ako se ovako budeš ponašao,

1025
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:29,880
 vraćamo te kući prvim autobusom.

1026
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:33,720
 Kažem, nemojte, molim vas,

1027
00:34:33,720 --> 00:34:35,080
 ubit će me mamu od batina.

1028
00:34:37,160 --> 00:34:38,900
 Ja sad, svako pomisli,

1029
00:34:38,900 --> 00:34:40,720
 možda će ga mamu ubiti od batina.

1030
00:34:40,720 --> 00:34:43,180
 A redko ko pomisli,

1031
00:34:43,180 --> 00:34:44,780
 možda manipuliše i sa mnom.

1032
00:34:44,780 --> 00:34:46,700
 Kažem, dobro,

1033
00:34:46,700 --> 00:34:48,980
 neću te vratiti kući.

1034
00:34:48,980 --> 00:34:51,820
 Ali ako se ovako budeš ponašao,

1035
00:34:51,820 --> 00:34:53,600
 ovo ti je žuti karton.

1036
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:56,120
 To će ti biti srveni,

1037
00:34:56,120 --> 00:34:56,860
 ideš kući.

1038
00:34:56,860 --> 00:34:58,260
 Nemora autobus,

1039
00:34:58,260 --> 00:34:59,400
 evo ja ću da te vozim.

1040
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:01,200
 Ili ću svati mamu da dođe po tebe.

1041
00:35:01,200 --> 00:35:03,360
 Nemojte, ali onda se kontroliši.

1042
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:06,260
 Ako ti dođe to nešto,

1043
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,400
 vidim ja taj neki impuls,

1044
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:08,880
 idi trči u svoju sobu,

1045
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:09,920
 pa tamo vrišti.

1046
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:12,840
 I već popodne.

1047
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:14,900
 Bili smo u kuhinju,

1048
00:35:14,900 --> 00:35:16,500
 čekali smo jer neko voće da uzmu,

1049
00:35:16,500 --> 00:35:18,460
 vidim ja njegom kreće da se namješta

1050
00:35:18,460 --> 00:35:20,880
 i sprint u sobu.

1051
00:35:20,880 --> 00:35:22,020
 Ja za njim.

1052
00:35:22,020 --> 00:35:24,280
 On ulazi u sobu,

1053
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:25,160
 kreće da vrišti.

1054
00:35:25,160 --> 00:35:27,220
 Vrata sočkinota, gledam.

1055
00:35:27,220 --> 00:35:30,820
 On vrišti, otvara plakar,

1056
00:35:30,820 --> 00:35:31,700
 uzima knjigu

1057
00:35:31,700 --> 00:35:33,420
 i kreće da liste knjigu

1058
00:35:33,420 --> 00:35:34,100
 i smiri se.

1059
00:35:34,100 --> 00:35:35,240
 Kažem, kako je to knjiga,

1060
00:35:35,240 --> 00:35:36,100
 čarobna knjiga,

1061
00:35:36,100 --> 00:35:38,000
 kad ga ona smirila.

1062
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:39,700
 Ulazim u sobu se,

1063
00:35:39,700 --> 00:35:40,400
 dobro jesam.

1064
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:41,520
 Šta to čitaš?

1065
00:35:41,520 --> 00:35:45,560
 To su slike

1066
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:47,040
 iz neke videoigrice.

1067
00:35:47,040 --> 00:35:49,200
 On gleda slike

1068
00:35:49,200 --> 00:35:49,760
 iz videoigrice

1069
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:50,480
 i smirio se.

1070
00:35:52,520 --> 00:35:52,760
 dobro.

1071
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:53,760
 Ja sad pitam,

1072
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:55,740
 te od njegove sobe su prijatelji

1073
00:35:55,740 --> 00:35:56,980
 iz istog dela grada su.

1074
00:35:56,980 --> 00:35:59,060
 Pitam, recite mi,

1075
00:35:59,060 --> 00:36:00,200
 kako se on ponašao?

1076
00:36:00,200 --> 00:36:01,000
 Pa kaže isto.

1077
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:02,380
 A što radice?

1078
00:36:02,380 --> 00:36:03,520
 Sada vidim tu videoigricu

1079
00:36:03,520 --> 00:36:04,080
 da ima knjigu.

1080
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:05,260
 A pa on igra videoigrice

1081
00:36:05,260 --> 00:36:05,720
 po sedem,

1082
00:36:05,720 --> 00:36:06,220
 osam sati,

1083
00:36:06,220 --> 00:36:07,260
 on se ne igra sa nama.

1084
00:36:07,260 --> 00:36:09,380
 To znači on igra sedem,

1085
00:36:09,380 --> 00:36:10,540
 osam sati videoigricu

1086
00:36:10,540 --> 00:36:11,280
 kad ide u školu,

1087
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:11,880
 kad spava.

1088
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:13,160
 I ja svatim,

1089
00:36:13,160 --> 00:36:13,640
 pa to je

1090
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:15,820
 ovisnost ili zavisnost

1091
00:36:15,820 --> 00:36:16,600
 od videoigrice.

1092
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:18,420
 agresivno ponašanje.

1093
00:36:18,420 --> 00:36:20,840
 Nemo osjećaj za druge.

1094
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:22,700
 Samo da dobiju to što želi.

1095
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:24,780
 I malo sam tu kontrolisao.

1096
00:36:24,780 --> 00:36:27,860
 I pišem posle kampu,

1097
00:36:27,860 --> 00:36:28,740
 obično roditeljima,

1098
00:36:28,740 --> 00:36:29,720
 pošaljemo pismo.

1099
00:36:29,720 --> 00:36:32,880
 Da se deto uklopilo,

1100
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:33,900
 da se nije uklopilo,

1101
00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:35,400
 da smo videli da je tu dobro,

1102
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:36,160
 da ovde nije dobro

1103
00:36:36,160 --> 00:36:37,300
 da malo to pojačuju.

1104
00:36:37,300 --> 00:36:38,960
 Pišem pismo da smo to primetili,

1105
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:39,940
 ali ja lepo napišem

1106
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:41,600
 da bi dobro bilo

1107
00:36:41,600 --> 00:36:42,620
 da upišo na sport.

1108
00:36:42,620 --> 00:36:45,020
 Da pokazuje znake

1109
00:36:45,020 --> 00:36:46,300
 zavisnosti od videoigrice.

1110
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:48,440
 Šta je mama odgovorila?

1111
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:49,040
 Šta mislite?

1112
00:36:49,040 --> 00:36:53,160
 Šta mislite?

1113
00:36:53,160 --> 00:36:53,840
 Evo sad ste vi

1114
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:55,300
 ranko i postavite pismo

1115
00:36:55,300 --> 00:36:55,860
 jednoj ženi

1116
00:36:55,860 --> 00:36:57,020
 da joj pomognete za sina.

1117
00:36:57,020 --> 00:36:58,340
 I šta je mama odgovorila?

1118
00:36:58,340 --> 00:36:59,680
 Evo ovo pitanje.

1119
00:36:59,680 --> 00:37:00,460
 Svi ko nas gledaju,

1120
00:37:00,460 --> 00:37:01,520
 evo i vi probajte

1121
00:37:01,520 --> 00:37:02,040
 da govorite

1122
00:37:02,040 --> 00:37:02,840
 šta je ta žena

1123
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:03,700
 meni napisala.

1124
00:37:03,700 --> 00:37:05,480
 A lepo sam pismo napisao

1125
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:06,900
 da malo smanje vidi

1126
00:37:06,900 --> 00:37:08,360
 ingrice da gupiše na sport.

1127
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:10,700
 Šta je ona odgovorila?

1128
00:37:10,700 --> 00:37:11,640
 Napala vas?

1129
00:37:11,640 --> 00:37:13,140
 Ili je?

1130
00:37:13,140 --> 00:37:14,660
 Kako?

1131
00:37:14,660 --> 00:37:16,520
 Kako me napala?

1132
00:37:16,600 --> 00:37:17,440
 Jeste na Falome.

1133
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:21,140
 Pa kritizirali ste nju zapravo?

1134
00:37:21,140 --> 00:37:22,740
 Napisale.

1135
00:37:22,740 --> 00:37:24,660
 Moj sin,

1136
00:37:24,660 --> 00:37:26,060
 moje zlato,

1137
00:37:26,060 --> 00:37:27,280
 moje blago.

1138
00:37:27,280 --> 00:37:29,040
 Pa njega svi vole,

1139
00:37:29,040 --> 00:37:29,940
 svi govore

1140
00:37:29,940 --> 00:37:30,860
 kako je to dobro,

1141
00:37:30,860 --> 00:37:31,320
 dete,

1142
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:32,820
 ja sa vama vero,

1143
00:37:32,820 --> 00:37:33,800
 ali vi ste jedini

1144
00:37:33,800 --> 00:37:34,320
 napisali

1145
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:35,300
 da ona ima neki problem.

1146
00:37:35,300 --> 00:37:36,460
 Kako to možete?

1147
00:37:36,460 --> 00:37:37,360
 Znači,

1148
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:38,420
 drvlje, kamenje.

1149
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:41,120
 I onda napišem drugo pismo.

1150
00:37:41,120 --> 00:37:42,520
 Kako god hoćete.

1151
00:37:42,520 --> 00:37:45,420
 Ali deco ko već pokazuju

1152
00:37:45,420 --> 00:37:45,900
 zavisnost,

1153
00:37:45,900 --> 00:37:47,400
 ovisnost u devetoj,

1154
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:48,300
 desetoj godini,

1155
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:50,540
 već po istraživanjima

1156
00:37:50,540 --> 00:37:51,440
 će tražiti

1157
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:52,360
 novu stimulaciju,

1158
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:52,540
 gde?

1159
00:37:52,540 --> 00:37:54,320
 Pa možda u narkoticima sutra.

1160
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:56,460
 Izgubit ćemo decu.

1161
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,740
 Roditelji često ne prihvati

1162
00:37:58,740 --> 00:37:59,300
 o kritiku.

1163
00:37:59,300 --> 00:38:00,600
 I zato kažem,

1164
00:38:00,600 --> 00:38:02,200
 roditelji je odgovoran

1165
00:38:02,200 --> 00:38:03,040
 za odgoj.

1166
00:38:03,040 --> 00:38:04,700
 Dete je krenulo u školu.

1167
00:38:04,700 --> 00:38:05,820
 Ko prvi vidi

1168
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:06,580
 da nešto ne u redu

1169
00:38:06,580 --> 00:38:07,280
 sa decetom

1170
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:09,500
 među 25 ili 30 učenika?

1171
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:10,480
 Učiteljica.

1172
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:12,740
 I to treba svaki roditelj

1173
00:38:12,740 --> 00:38:13,140
 da zna.

1174
00:38:13,140 --> 00:38:14,780
 Učiteljica je poslednja

1175
00:38:14,780 --> 00:38:15,780
 ona linija

1176
00:38:15,780 --> 00:38:16,660
 koja može

1177
00:38:16,660 --> 00:38:17,780
 da urode neku reakciju

1178
00:38:17,780 --> 00:38:18,740
 da pomogne detetu.

1179
00:38:18,740 --> 00:38:21,120
 Ako mi priječamo

1180
00:38:21,120 --> 00:38:23,100
 da učiteljica nije dobra,

1181
00:38:23,100 --> 00:38:24,920
 da ona ne znam svoj posao,

1182
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:26,240
 da ko zna

1183
00:38:26,240 --> 00:38:27,160
 kakva je

1184
00:38:27,160 --> 00:38:28,320
 i roditelji

1185
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:29,460
 svašta priča učiteljima.

1186
00:38:29,460 --> 00:38:31,940
 Učenik tog sekunda

1187
00:38:31,940 --> 00:38:33,160
 gubi respekt.

1188
00:38:33,160 --> 00:38:35,380
 Ko će njemu pomoći?

1189
00:38:35,380 --> 00:38:37,480
 Pa niko.

1190
00:38:37,480 --> 00:38:38,920
 Pa li imate roditelji,

1191
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:39,780
 teri učitelje

1192
00:38:39,780 --> 00:38:41,940
 da poklonu ocenu?

1193
00:38:41,940 --> 00:38:44,300
 Ne sa četvorke na peticu,

1194
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:45,440
 sa trojke na peticu.

1195
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:48,200
 Kao da će to nešto pomoći.

1196
00:38:48,200 --> 00:38:49,540
 Dupišu, ne znam šta.

1197
00:38:49,540 --> 00:38:50,580
 Pa je se desilo

1198
00:38:50,580 --> 00:38:51,740
 od Crne Gori pre pet godina,

1199
00:38:51,740 --> 00:38:53,240
 često pokažem na predavanju.

1200
00:38:53,240 --> 00:38:55,400
 Od 102 kandidata

1201
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:56,780
 za upis na medicinske fakulte,

1202
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:59,700
 u te 90 nije položilo

1203
00:38:59,700 --> 00:39:00,420
 prijemni ispit.

1204
00:39:00,420 --> 00:39:02,280
 A to su najbolji učenici

1205
00:39:02,280 --> 00:39:02,860
 Crne Gore.

1206
00:39:02,860 --> 00:39:04,640
 I sad pitanje,

1207
00:39:04,640 --> 00:39:05,640
 kakve su to petice?

1208
00:39:05,640 --> 00:39:07,580
 I čak su pitali ministra,

1209
00:39:07,580 --> 00:39:08,760
 novinari su bili,

1210
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:11,040
 pa šta se to dogodilo?

1211
00:39:11,040 --> 00:39:14,460
 Šta je on odgovario?

1212
00:39:14,460 --> 00:39:15,420
 Tek to mi je bilo.

1213
00:39:15,420 --> 00:39:16,420
 Šta bi vi odgovarili

1214
00:39:16,420 --> 00:39:17,220
 da ste ministar?

1215
00:39:17,220 --> 00:39:18,220
 Šta se to dogodilo?

1216
00:39:18,220 --> 00:39:22,120
 Sad nekaj roditelji

1217
00:39:22,120 --> 00:39:23,500
 pomisli šta je rekao ministar

1218
00:39:23,500 --> 00:39:25,320
 o odgovoran za obrazovanje.

1219
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:26,620
 I pitali ga čoče,

1220
00:39:26,620 --> 00:39:27,700
 gospodine ministar,

1221
00:39:27,700 --> 00:39:28,580
 šta se to dogodilo?

1222
00:39:28,580 --> 00:39:29,920
 102 kandidata,

1223
00:39:29,920 --> 00:39:31,340
 najbolji učenici Crne Gore

1224
00:39:31,340 --> 00:39:32,280
 90 nije položilo

1225
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:32,920
 prijemni ispit.

1226
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:35,240
 Ajde.

1227
00:39:35,240 --> 00:39:37,700
 To je dokaz

1228
00:39:37,700 --> 00:39:39,320
 da je škola napreduje.

1229
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:41,200
 Pa nazadu je lišta?

1230
00:39:41,200 --> 00:39:42,040
 Evo sad vi ste ministar.

1231
00:39:42,040 --> 00:39:42,060
 Ne, ne, ne.

1232
00:39:42,060 --> 00:39:43,340
 Možda bi on odgovorio

1233
00:39:43,340 --> 00:39:44,180
 da je to dokaz

1234
00:39:44,180 --> 00:39:45,340
 da je škola napreduje.

1235
00:39:45,340 --> 00:39:46,740
 Kom smislu napreduje?

1236
00:39:46,740 --> 00:39:47,200
 Evo ja sam ovinu.

1237
00:39:47,200 --> 00:39:48,800
 Da su stroži,

1238
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:50,040
 stroži su uvjeti.

1239
00:39:50,040 --> 00:39:51,580
 Pa da li on imaju

1240
00:39:51,580 --> 00:39:52,160
 srpetici?

1241
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:54,000
 U srednjoj školi.

1242
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:54,360
 Da.

1243
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,980
 A ne mogu da polože prijemni?

1244
00:39:55,980 --> 00:39:57,900
 Ne znam kako je odgovorio.

1245
00:39:57,900 --> 00:40:00,960
 Imate na YouTube-u.

1246
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:01,240
 On je odgovorio.

1247
00:40:01,240 --> 00:40:02,080
 Ja pošto ne osjećam

1248
00:40:02,080 --> 00:40:02,920
 tu njegovu odgovornost.

1249
00:40:02,920 --> 00:40:04,000
 Ne znam kako je odgovorio.

1250
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:04,580
 Ne, on je ovako rekao.

1251
00:40:04,580 --> 00:40:05,180
 Ko zna,

1252
00:40:05,180 --> 00:40:05,820
 od prilike,

1253
00:40:05,820 --> 00:40:06,600
 parafraziram,

1254
00:40:06,600 --> 00:40:08,280
 ko zna kakav su

1255
00:40:08,280 --> 00:40:09,400
 prijemni spremili

1256
00:40:09,400 --> 00:40:10,600
 našim učenicima?

1257
00:40:10,600 --> 00:40:11,900
 Kao da je neko

1258
00:40:11,900 --> 00:40:13,160
 podvalio prijemni ispit.

1259
00:40:13,160 --> 00:40:14,300
 Pa je uvredio

1260
00:40:14,300 --> 00:40:15,600
 profesora na medicine,

1261
00:40:15,600 --> 00:40:16,280
 neki pozdaj,

1262
00:40:16,280 --> 00:40:16,900
 pa su oni rekli

1263
00:40:16,900 --> 00:40:18,560
 ne, nije prijemni teži.

1264
00:40:18,560 --> 00:40:20,100
 Isti je.

1265
00:40:20,100 --> 00:40:21,220
 Nego su nam učenici

1266
00:40:21,220 --> 00:40:21,940
 sve slabiji.

1267
00:40:21,940 --> 00:40:23,240
 I sad svi ko nas gledaju

1268
00:40:23,240 --> 00:40:23,900
 neka pomisle.

1269
00:40:23,900 --> 00:40:25,020
 Šta je onda

1270
00:40:25,020 --> 00:40:26,300
 odgovor pod A?

1271
00:40:26,300 --> 00:40:27,780
 Da je prijemni

1272
00:40:27,780 --> 00:40:28,380
 sve teži,

1273
00:40:28,380 --> 00:40:28,780
 teži,

1274
00:40:28,780 --> 00:40:29,220
 teži,

1275
00:40:29,220 --> 00:40:29,700
 ili B?

1276
00:40:29,700 --> 00:40:31,580
 Da su učenici slabiji,

1277
00:40:31,580 --> 00:40:32,440
 slabiji, slabiji.

1278
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:34,040
 I šta je A ili B?

1279
00:40:34,040 --> 00:40:36,340
 Da, onda je zapravo

1280
00:40:36,340 --> 00:40:37,280
 pitanje da li je

1281
00:40:37,280 --> 00:40:37,980
 srednja škola

1282
00:40:37,980 --> 00:40:39,220
 prilagođena

1283
00:40:39,220 --> 00:40:40,220
 njihovoj razini.

1284
00:40:40,220 --> 00:40:40,860
 Čili zapravo

1285
00:40:40,860 --> 00:40:41,580
 srednja škola je

1286
00:40:41,580 --> 00:40:42,360
 prelagana, je li?

1287
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:43,540
 Pa ne samo da je

1288
00:40:43,540 --> 00:40:44,020
 prelagana,

1289
00:40:44,020 --> 00:40:45,300
 nego socija ne poklanjaju.

1290
00:40:45,300 --> 00:40:46,440
 Ne moguće da imaju

1291
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:47,080
 sve petice.

1292
00:40:47,080 --> 00:40:48,540
 Ali nije onda problem

1293
00:40:48,540 --> 00:40:49,240
 ni srednja škola,

1294
00:40:49,240 --> 00:40:49,980
 pa oni su takvi

1295
00:40:49,980 --> 00:40:51,220
 stigli u srednju školu.

1296
00:40:51,780 --> 00:40:53,400
 Mi sad imamo situaciju

1297
00:40:53,400 --> 00:40:54,920
 da i osnovna škola,

1298
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:56,780
 već kasni,

1299
00:40:56,780 --> 00:40:57,160
 zašto?

1300
00:40:57,160 --> 00:40:58,300
 Pa nam je već,

1301
00:40:58,300 --> 00:40:59,840
 u nas za 10-15 godina,

1302
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,820
 svaka nova generacija

1303
00:41:01,820 --> 00:41:03,200
 upisana u prvi razred

1304
00:41:03,200 --> 00:41:04,000
 malo slabija,

1305
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,080
 u odnosu na prethodne,

1306
00:41:05,080 --> 00:41:06,100
 da je učitelji to vide.

1307
00:41:06,100 --> 00:41:08,120
 Iako nama svaka nova generacija

1308
00:41:08,120 --> 00:41:09,420
 slabija, slabija, slabija,

1309
00:41:09,420 --> 00:41:10,880
 kad upisaju prvi razred,

1310
00:41:10,880 --> 00:41:12,960
 po učiteljima,

1311
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:14,560
 ako i stignu za dvjeti godine

1312
00:41:14,560 --> 00:41:15,460
 da malo podignu

1313
00:41:15,460 --> 00:41:16,440
 na nekadašnji nivo,

1314
00:41:16,440 --> 00:41:18,340
 onda kreću u peti razred,

1315
00:41:18,340 --> 00:41:19,660
 pa kreću u gimnaziju.

1316
00:41:19,660 --> 00:41:21,540
 Znači, mi moramo da shvatimo

1317
00:41:21,540 --> 00:41:23,920
 da je mozak 90 i više

1318
00:41:23,920 --> 00:41:25,660
 posto završio svoj razvoj

1319
00:41:25,660 --> 00:41:27,260
 do peti, šesti godine.

1320
00:41:27,260 --> 00:41:29,660
 Iako oni slabiji kreću u školu,

1321
00:41:29,660 --> 00:41:32,400
 malo je tu prostor za popravak.

1322
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:34,060
 E, tu je problem.

1323
00:41:34,060 --> 00:41:36,800
 Naša deca nisu razvila

1324
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:38,480
 duboke regije mozga,

1325
00:41:38,480 --> 00:41:39,820
 kreću tako i u školu,

1326
00:41:39,820 --> 00:41:40,440
 onda dolazimo,

1327
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:42,320
 pa najvažniji period je

1328
00:41:42,320 --> 00:41:44,900
 pa od 30 do šesti godine.

1329
00:41:44,900 --> 00:41:46,740
 Oni moraju da krenu u školu

1330
00:41:46,740 --> 00:41:47,900
 spremni, da znaju da sede,

1331
00:41:47,900 --> 00:41:49,280
 da pišu, da čitaju,

1332
00:41:49,380 --> 00:41:49,980
 da slušaju,

1333
00:41:49,980 --> 00:41:50,920
 da pamte.

1334
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:52,420
 Onda učitelj može da radi.

1335
00:41:52,420 --> 00:41:54,980
 Ako naši učenici to ne mogu,

1336
00:41:54,980 --> 00:41:57,960
 kako će učitelj da im pomogne?

1337
00:41:57,960 --> 00:41:59,500
 Već sad imamo evo u Hrvatskoj

1338
00:41:59,500 --> 00:42:01,880
 i u drugim državama regije,

1339
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:03,260
 ali u Hrvatskoj 10% generacije

1340
00:42:03,260 --> 00:42:05,640
 ne može da krene u prvi razred,

1341
00:42:05,640 --> 00:42:07,260
 traže se odlaganje godinu dana.

1342
00:42:07,260 --> 00:42:10,600
 A još 20% treba dodatno pomoć

1343
00:42:10,600 --> 00:42:13,520
 psihologa, pedagoga, defektologa.

1344
00:42:13,520 --> 00:42:14,680
 pa šta je ovo?

1345
00:42:14,680 --> 00:42:16,920
 Iako ne budemo ništa promenili,

1346
00:42:16,920 --> 00:42:18,320
 sad je to pitanje ovako,

1347
00:42:18,320 --> 00:42:20,660
 da li se deca postati bolja?

1348
00:42:20,660 --> 00:42:22,060
 Nemoguće.

1349
00:42:22,060 --> 00:42:24,000
 Znači moramo nešto da menjamo kad.

1350
00:42:24,440 --> 00:42:26,160
 Po periodu vitezenog razvoja mozga

1351
00:42:26,160 --> 00:42:27,440
 od treće do šeste godine,

1352
00:42:27,440 --> 00:42:29,620
 tu pravimo velike propuste.

1353
00:42:29,620 --> 00:42:32,260
 I tu su nam roditelji odgovorni,

1354
00:42:32,260 --> 00:42:33,100
 nisu krivi,

1355
00:42:33,100 --> 00:42:35,540
 a sistem vrtiće moraju da poprave.

1356
00:42:35,540 --> 00:42:37,700
 I tu ima šest nekih faktora

1357
00:42:37,700 --> 00:42:39,980
 zašto su deca sve slabije.

1358
00:42:39,980 --> 00:42:41,540
 Znači mi moramo prvo da gledamo

1359
00:42:41,540 --> 00:42:43,060
 razvoju mozga do šeste godine.

1360
00:42:43,060 --> 00:42:44,780
 Od idemo prvi razred,

1361
00:42:44,780 --> 00:42:46,720
 da idemo metode

1362
00:42:46,720 --> 00:42:48,720
 kako da nauče

1363
00:42:48,720 --> 00:42:50,900
 da umemorišu gradevo,

1364
00:42:50,900 --> 00:42:52,320
 kako to da rade kroz metode

1365
00:42:52,320 --> 00:42:53,120
 količane igru.

1366
00:42:53,740 --> 00:42:54,960
 E onda oni mogu dalje da idu.

1367
00:42:54,960 --> 00:42:57,700
 Pa će doći na fakultet malo spremniji.

1368
00:42:57,700 --> 00:42:59,040
 Ovako kako je sad.

1369
00:42:59,040 --> 00:43:00,060
 Pitanje je,

1370
00:43:00,060 --> 00:43:02,140
 jel sad za medicinu u Podgorici,

1371
00:43:02,140 --> 00:43:03,940
 pa ko će nas sutra da leči?

1372
00:43:03,940 --> 00:43:06,620
 Ko će da pravi mostove, tunele?

1373
00:43:06,620 --> 00:43:07,660
 Kinezi?

1374
00:43:07,660 --> 00:43:09,200
 Gde smo mi?

1375
00:43:09,200 --> 00:43:12,420
 Znači, jako je ozbiljno sad ovo,

1376
00:43:12,420 --> 00:43:13,940
 jer vreme za reforme

1377
00:43:13,940 --> 00:43:15,320
 nama je već polako prošlo.

1378
00:43:15,320 --> 00:43:16,940
 I tu moram reći,

1379
00:43:16,940 --> 00:43:18,740
 ljudi ne sveti ukoliko vreme brzo ide.

1380
00:43:18,740 --> 00:43:20,840
 Mi u Sloveniji imamo,

1381
00:43:20,840 --> 00:43:21,900
 tamo predajem,

1382
00:43:23,040 --> 00:43:25,480
 epohalne otkriće su stoletna otkrića.

1383
00:43:25,480 --> 00:43:26,180
 Šta to znači?

1384
00:43:26,180 --> 00:43:28,300
 Jednom u sto leta.

1385
00:43:28,300 --> 00:43:30,740
 A danas koliko čest imamo ta otkrića?

1386
00:43:30,740 --> 00:43:32,460
 Pa jedno godišnje.

1387
00:43:32,460 --> 00:43:33,540
 To znači,

1388
00:43:33,540 --> 00:43:35,420
 u broje otkriće se toliko brzo povećava.

1389
00:43:35,420 --> 00:43:36,880
 Znači, da vreme brže ide,

1390
00:43:36,880 --> 00:43:38,620
 da se jako puno stvari dešava

1391
00:43:38,620 --> 00:43:39,880
 u jedinici vremena,

1392
00:43:39,880 --> 00:43:40,560
 nego ranije.

1393
00:43:41,920 --> 00:43:43,420
 A to znači samo jedno.

1394
00:43:43,420 --> 00:43:46,200
 Ako je država nekad nastajala

1395
00:43:46,200 --> 00:43:48,380
 i nestajala za 500 godina,

1396
00:43:48,380 --> 00:43:50,780
 to će danas biti za 50.

1397
00:43:50,780 --> 00:43:54,240
 Šta ako imamo 20, 30 generacija

1398
00:43:54,240 --> 00:43:57,360
 slabije sposobne dece ili nesposobne dece?

1399
00:43:58,000 --> 00:43:59,520
 Pa druge narodi nas prekrivaju.

1400
00:43:59,520 --> 00:44:00,620
 To znači,

1401
00:44:00,620 --> 00:44:03,460
 obrazovanje je stup društva.

1402
00:44:03,460 --> 00:44:04,280
 Uvijek je bilo.

1403
00:44:04,280 --> 00:44:06,140
 A će sad da se vidi jako brzo.

1404
00:44:06,140 --> 00:44:08,800
 Nema tu vremena 10-20 godina za reforme.

1405
00:44:08,800 --> 00:44:10,560
 I ono što predem,

1406
00:44:10,560 --> 00:44:11,680
 a predem po celu Evropi,

1407
00:44:11,680 --> 00:44:12,880
 sad idem Kanada, Amerike,

1408
00:44:12,880 --> 00:44:14,240
 o treći put za godinu dana,

1409
00:44:14,240 --> 00:44:16,100
 reforme ne mogu više

1410
00:44:16,100 --> 00:44:18,220
 ili možda mogu na nevou države

1411
00:44:18,220 --> 00:44:19,580
 okvirna reforma

1412
00:44:19,580 --> 00:44:21,560
 i u hodu da se rešava.

1413
00:44:21,560 --> 00:44:24,160
 Da čak mislim da će svaki grad,

1414
00:44:24,160 --> 00:44:26,120
 svaka regija morati da brine za sebe.

1415
00:44:26,120 --> 00:44:28,000
 To da čekamo rješenje,

1416
00:44:28,000 --> 00:44:28,820
 državni nivo,

1417
00:44:28,820 --> 00:44:30,300
 pet pilot projekata,

1418
00:44:30,300 --> 00:44:31,420
 idemo 10 godina,

1419
00:44:31,420 --> 00:44:33,520
 jesmo pogrešili jednu setnicu,

1420
00:44:33,520 --> 00:44:34,100
 gotovi smo.

1421
00:44:34,100 --> 00:44:36,680
 Či morat će u hodu da se radi reforma.

1422
00:44:36,680 --> 00:44:39,040
 Eto, to predem na fakultetu,

1423
00:44:39,040 --> 00:44:40,880
 znači neuroznanost,

1424
00:44:40,880 --> 00:44:42,500
 uzgoj in izobraževanju,

1425
00:44:42,500 --> 00:44:43,380
 odgoj i obrazovanju,

1426
00:44:43,380 --> 00:44:46,080
 moramo da učimo buduće naše pedagoge,

1427
00:44:46,080 --> 00:44:47,600
 psihologe, učitelje,

1428
00:44:48,000 --> 00:44:51,140
 kako da oni u hodu rešavaju probleme.

1429
00:44:51,140 --> 00:44:55,280
 Koja je onda zapravo fundamentalna razlika

1430
00:44:55,280 --> 00:44:56,120
 između generacije?

1431
00:44:56,120 --> 00:44:59,260
 Recimo, u doba kaste vi bili djete

1432
00:44:59,260 --> 00:45:01,720
 ili danas recimo kad je možnje?

1433
00:45:01,720 --> 00:45:05,020
 A što je fundamentalna razlika uopće?

1434
00:45:05,020 --> 00:45:06,580
 Sad ću reći formiranje mozga,

1435
00:45:06,580 --> 00:45:08,120
 znači drugače ponašanje,

1436
00:45:08,120 --> 00:45:10,580
 drugače vrednosti života,

1437
00:45:10,580 --> 00:45:12,940
 znači nepotpuno drugače

1438
00:45:12,940 --> 00:45:14,760
 percepiraju društvo

1439
00:45:14,760 --> 00:45:19,040
 i recimo neke stvari nego mi.

1440
00:45:19,040 --> 00:45:20,240
 Zašto?

1441
00:45:20,240 --> 00:45:23,260
 Jel ako je okruženje važno 100%,

1442
00:45:23,260 --> 00:45:24,200
 a reku sam da je,

1443
00:45:24,200 --> 00:45:25,880
 znači genetika je važna,

1444
00:45:25,880 --> 00:45:26,940
 100% to je potencijal.

1445
00:45:26,940 --> 00:45:29,160
 A razum mozga zavisa od okruženja,

1446
00:45:29,160 --> 00:45:29,420
 kad?

1447
00:45:29,420 --> 00:45:30,840
 Pa tog se forivera mozak,

1448
00:45:30,840 --> 00:45:31,900
 prve 3-4 godine.

1449
00:45:31,900 --> 00:45:33,640
 Znači okruženje je ključno,

1450
00:45:33,640 --> 00:45:35,200
 pa čak je do 5-7.

1451
00:45:35,200 --> 00:45:38,020
 I sad, samo da bih to objasnio,

1452
00:45:39,260 --> 00:45:42,240
 zašto je za mozak genetika 100% okruženje 100%,

1453
00:45:42,240 --> 00:45:43,440
 a za boju očiju,

1454
00:45:43,440 --> 00:45:46,540
 genetika je 100% okruženje nula.

1455
00:45:46,540 --> 00:45:49,080
 Sad ljudi budu zbunjeni,

1456
00:45:49,080 --> 00:45:52,100
 kako mislite za mozak 100% jedno 100% drugo,

1457
00:45:52,100 --> 00:45:53,660
 a za boju očiju,

1458
00:45:53,660 --> 00:45:55,340
 pa genetika je 100%,

1459
00:45:55,340 --> 00:45:58,020
 i onda objasnim za mozak.

1460
00:45:58,020 --> 00:45:59,980
 Mi kad se rodimo,

1461
00:45:59,980 --> 00:46:01,400
 mozak nije završao razvoj,

1462
00:46:01,400 --> 00:46:02,300
 to je siva masa,

1463
00:46:02,300 --> 00:46:03,940
 to nema nernih puteva.

1464
00:46:03,940 --> 00:46:05,960
 I te kad se rodimo,

1465
00:46:05,960 --> 00:46:07,180
 kreću nerni putevi.

1466
00:46:07,180 --> 00:46:08,920
 Pitanje je,

1467
00:46:08,920 --> 00:46:11,820
 zašto naš mozak nije završao razvoj

1468
00:46:11,820 --> 00:46:12,500
 u trudnoći?

1469
00:46:12,500 --> 00:46:14,340
 Rećemo, druga živa bića.

1470
00:46:14,340 --> 00:46:16,740
 Za par sati, za par dana

1471
00:46:16,740 --> 00:46:18,680
 su operativna mala žirafa.

1472
00:46:18,680 --> 00:46:20,940
 Ona mora da stane na noge

1473
00:46:20,940 --> 00:46:23,020
 jako brzo da krene da trče za mamom.

1474
00:46:23,020 --> 00:46:23,760
 Zašto?

1475
00:46:24,460 --> 00:46:25,540
 Pa pošće lavovi.

1476
00:46:25,540 --> 00:46:28,260
 A mi,

1477
00:46:28,260 --> 00:46:30,140
 po profesoru Lichtmanu,

1478
00:46:30,140 --> 00:46:30,940
 sa Harvarda,

1479
00:46:30,940 --> 00:46:32,860
 mi smo fetusi do 13. godine.

1480
00:46:32,860 --> 00:46:35,280
 Kako nismo si tako tvrdni,

1481
00:46:35,280 --> 00:46:36,380
 a čovjek će možda dobiti

1482
00:46:36,380 --> 00:46:37,500
 i Nobelovu nagradu,

1483
00:46:37,500 --> 00:46:39,260
 kako fetusi do 13. godine?

1484
00:46:39,260 --> 00:46:41,240
 Pa zato što nama treba

1485
00:46:41,240 --> 00:46:42,740
 tuđaj pomoć da bi preživjeli.

1486
00:46:42,740 --> 00:46:45,140
 I u stvari,

1487
00:46:45,140 --> 00:46:48,160
 tu je odgovor na sve to što sad pričam.

1488
00:46:48,160 --> 00:46:50,120
 Pa naš mozak je jako velik.

1489
00:46:50,120 --> 00:46:53,160
 Ne može da završi razvoj u trudnoći.

1490
00:46:53,580 --> 00:46:54,220
 Zašto?

1491
00:46:54,220 --> 00:46:56,520
 Pa ako bi mozg bio malo veći,

1492
00:46:56,520 --> 00:46:59,460
 onda bi glava bila pa malo veća

1493
00:46:59,460 --> 00:47:01,000
 i ne bi mogli da se rodimo.

1494
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:03,480
 To znači mi ljudi se rađimo kad

1495
00:47:03,480 --> 00:47:05,280
 u poslednjem momentu

1496
00:47:05,280 --> 00:47:06,940
 doga glava može da prođe

1497
00:47:06,940 --> 00:47:08,120
 kroz porođeni kanal.

1498
00:47:08,820 --> 00:47:10,100
 Čak imamo dve fontanela

1499
00:47:10,100 --> 00:47:11,400
 da se ta glava stisne.

1500
00:47:11,400 --> 00:47:13,940
 I onda kreće razvoj mozga.

1501
00:47:13,940 --> 00:47:15,480
 Od čega zavisi?

1502
00:47:15,480 --> 00:47:16,580
 Od okruženja.

1503
00:47:16,580 --> 00:47:18,240
 I tada kreće formiranje

1504
00:47:18,240 --> 00:47:20,020
 nernih puteva i sinapsi.

1505
00:47:20,020 --> 00:47:21,540
 Pa čak profesorica

1506
00:47:21,540 --> 00:47:23,100
 Marian Daymond iz Kalifornije

1507
00:47:23,100 --> 00:47:23,600
 uradila,

1508
00:47:23,600 --> 00:47:25,220
 sad već čujan eksperiment,

1509
00:47:25,220 --> 00:47:27,420
 uzela je dve grupe

1510
00:47:27,420 --> 00:47:28,600
 genetski potpuno iste.

1511
00:47:29,440 --> 00:47:32,200
 Jedna grupa ima vodiju hranu,

1512
00:47:32,200 --> 00:47:33,440
 a druga grupa

1513
00:47:33,440 --> 00:47:35,540
 nema vodiju hranu,

1514
00:47:35,540 --> 00:47:36,420
 ima laverinte.

1515
00:47:36,420 --> 00:47:38,560
 Ona druga grupa mora da misli

1516
00:47:38,560 --> 00:47:40,020
 gde da skrene,

1517
00:47:40,020 --> 00:47:40,760
 gde da stane,

1518
00:47:40,760 --> 00:47:41,780
 gde da se provuče

1519
00:47:41,780 --> 00:47:42,980
 da bi došle do vode hrane.

1520
00:47:42,980 --> 00:47:45,640
 Kad su za, ne znam,

1521
00:47:45,640 --> 00:47:47,740
 15 dana završili eksperiment,

1522
00:47:47,740 --> 00:47:52,140
 grupa B je bila 50% inteligentnija.

1523
00:47:52,140 --> 00:47:53,400
 A genetski su isti.

1524
00:47:53,400 --> 00:47:55,540
 Šta dalje vidjeli ispod mikroskopa?

1525
00:47:55,540 --> 00:47:58,820
 Grupa B imala veći broj sinapsi

1526
00:47:58,820 --> 00:47:59,760
 od grupe A.

1527
00:47:59,760 --> 00:48:02,260
 Znači sad imamo dokaz

1528
00:48:02,260 --> 00:48:03,960
 da od tih sinapse,

1529
00:48:03,960 --> 00:48:05,940
 od tih veza zavisi inteligencija.

1530
00:48:05,940 --> 00:48:07,220
 I sad da poslijemo,

1531
00:48:07,220 --> 00:48:08,400
 šta su onda neuroni?

1532
00:48:08,400 --> 00:48:09,660
 Evo mi ljudi dobijemo

1533
00:48:09,660 --> 00:48:10,960
 100 milijarde neurona

1534
00:48:10,960 --> 00:48:12,080
 od mami i tate.

1535
00:48:12,080 --> 00:48:13,040
 To je genetika.

1536
00:48:13,040 --> 00:48:15,480
 A kako će se povezati?

1537
00:48:15,480 --> 00:48:17,260
 To su sinapse,

1538
00:48:17,260 --> 00:48:19,060
 to je okruženje.

1539
00:48:19,060 --> 00:48:20,240
 I sad razumijemo,

1540
00:48:20,240 --> 00:48:21,700
 genetika 100% okruženje,

1541
00:48:21,700 --> 00:48:22,640
 skoro 100%,

1542
00:48:22,640 --> 00:48:24,500
 jer neke sinapse,

1543
00:48:24,500 --> 00:48:25,120
 kad se rodimo,

1544
00:48:25,120 --> 00:48:26,600
 ostano većina se resorbuje.

1545
00:48:26,600 --> 00:48:28,580
 To znači okruženje,

1546
00:48:28,700 --> 00:48:31,400
 menja strukturu našeg mozga.

1547
00:48:31,400 --> 00:48:33,200
 I sad ne može biti isto

1548
00:48:33,200 --> 00:48:34,400
 neko ko se rodio

1549
00:48:34,400 --> 00:48:36,020
 pre 50 i više godina,

1550
00:48:36,020 --> 00:48:37,700
 jer su deca trčala

1551
00:48:37,700 --> 00:48:39,600
 nevno po 10-20 kilometara.

1552
00:48:39,600 --> 00:48:41,200
 Kretenje je jako važno.

1553
00:48:41,200 --> 00:48:42,700
 A danas,

1554
00:48:42,700 --> 00:48:44,460
 nema toliko kretenja.

1555
00:48:44,460 --> 00:48:45,700
 Evo kolica do druge,

1556
00:48:45,700 --> 00:48:46,400
 treće godine.

1557
00:48:47,860 --> 00:48:52,860
 pa pitajte neke starije ljudi od 70-80 godina,

1558
00:48:52,860 --> 00:48:55,160
 da li še imali kolice za svoje dete?

1559
00:48:55,160 --> 00:48:57,200
 Ako je imao svaka peta mama kolica,

1560
00:48:57,200 --> 00:48:58,520
 ako je imala i godinu dana,

1561
00:48:58,520 --> 00:48:59,480
 a danas,

1562
00:48:59,480 --> 00:49:02,040
 kolice do 34. godine.

1563
00:49:02,040 --> 00:49:03,560
 Nema kretenja.

1564
00:49:04,520 --> 00:49:06,480
 onda ne damo dete da padne,

1565
00:49:06,480 --> 00:49:07,700
 da se ne povredi.

1566
00:49:07,700 --> 00:49:09,960
 Ne damo da se penje na drvo.

1567
00:49:09,960 --> 00:49:13,240
 A mi smo se penjali po drveću,

1568
00:49:13,240 --> 00:49:14,480
 niko nije ni gledao šta radimo.

1569
00:49:15,180 --> 00:49:16,520
 sumo kažu dođite na ručak,

1570
00:49:16,520 --> 00:49:17,840
 dođite na večeru.

1571
00:49:17,840 --> 00:49:20,420
 Mi smo se penjali po drveću,

1572
00:49:20,420 --> 00:49:20,940
 skakali,

1573
00:49:20,940 --> 00:49:21,620
 priskakali,

1574
00:49:21,620 --> 00:49:22,300
 provlačili,

1575
00:49:22,300 --> 00:49:24,260
 hodili po nekim i višnjacima.

1576
00:49:24,260 --> 00:49:25,880
 Znači mi smo imali u tom kretenju

1577
00:49:25,880 --> 00:49:26,640
 njako puno stvari

1578
00:49:26,640 --> 00:49:27,720
 koje formiraju mozak.

1579
00:49:27,720 --> 00:49:29,360
 A naše dete danas

1580
00:49:29,360 --> 00:49:31,960
 ne sme da padne,

1581
00:49:31,960 --> 00:49:32,880
 ne sme da skače,

1582
00:49:32,880 --> 00:49:33,740
 ne sme na drveće,

1583
00:49:33,740 --> 00:49:34,640
 ne sme ni izbrdo.

1584
00:49:34,640 --> 00:49:37,340
 Pa da bi dete bilo sigurno,

1585
00:49:37,340 --> 00:49:38,840
 kupimo TV,

1586
00:49:38,840 --> 00:49:39,820
 usobjedimo TV

1587
00:49:39,820 --> 00:49:41,940
 i odjednom oduzimamo kretenje,

1588
00:49:41,940 --> 00:49:42,820
 istraživanje

1589
00:49:42,820 --> 00:49:45,400
 i dolazi do promjenu radu mozga.

1590
00:49:45,400 --> 00:49:47,660
 To znači da svaka,

1591
00:49:47,660 --> 00:49:49,360
 sad već na deset godina,

1592
00:49:49,360 --> 00:49:50,480
 kako se okruženje menja,

1593
00:49:50,480 --> 00:49:51,880
 drugačije je ponačanje

1594
00:49:51,880 --> 00:49:53,100
 svake nove generacije.

1595
00:49:53,100 --> 00:49:55,360
 I sad da vidim na ove generacije,

1596
00:49:55,360 --> 00:49:56,780
 mi kad smo radili pre deset godina,

1597
00:49:56,780 --> 00:49:58,260
 da već tada su učitelji

1598
00:49:58,260 --> 00:49:59,020
 govorili da su oni

1599
00:49:59,020 --> 00:49:59,960
 kognitivno slabiji.

1600
00:49:59,960 --> 00:50:01,240
 Pre deset godina.

1601
00:50:01,240 --> 00:50:03,240
 Dolaze na fakultet,

1602
00:50:03,240 --> 00:50:04,360
 nema predavno fakultetu.

1603
00:50:04,360 --> 00:50:05,920
 Dobro su deca.

1604
00:50:05,920 --> 00:50:08,100
 Imaju empatiju,

1605
00:50:08,100 --> 00:50:09,040
 osjećaj za druge,

1606
00:50:09,040 --> 00:50:10,380
 hoće da pomognu,

1607
00:50:10,380 --> 00:50:12,380
 ali kognitivno jesu slabiji.

1608
00:50:13,820 --> 00:50:15,440
 Nema tog rezonovanja visokog.

1609
00:50:15,440 --> 00:50:17,760
 I sad je naravno pitanje

1610
00:50:17,760 --> 00:50:18,980
 na celom društvu,

1611
00:50:18,980 --> 00:50:19,620
 šta ćemo mi,

1612
00:50:19,620 --> 00:50:21,200
 kompjuter su nas pobedili

1613
00:50:21,200 --> 00:50:22,760
 po informacijama i kombinacijama.

1614
00:50:22,760 --> 00:50:25,180
 Znači, učenje na pamet,

1615
00:50:25,180 --> 00:50:28,720
 to je učenje za prošlost.

1616
00:50:30,220 --> 00:50:31,520
 Mi moramo da učemo decu

1617
00:50:31,520 --> 00:50:32,900
 na drugačiji način,

1618
00:50:32,900 --> 00:50:34,200
 da razvimo kreativnost,

1619
00:50:34,200 --> 00:50:36,380
 da razvimo timski rad,

1620
00:50:36,380 --> 00:50:37,100
 nove ideje,

1621
00:50:37,100 --> 00:50:38,660
 da ekspremamo za budućnost.

1622
00:50:38,660 --> 00:50:40,100
 Tako da u nove generacije

1623
00:50:40,100 --> 00:50:41,740
 na neki način njesu oštećene,

1624
00:50:41,740 --> 00:50:43,280
 jer nisu kognitivno

1625
00:50:43,280 --> 00:50:45,080
 jaki kao mi.

1626
00:50:45,080 --> 00:50:46,740
 Ima dobre deca,

1627
00:50:46,740 --> 00:50:47,240
 ne kažem,

1628
00:50:47,240 --> 00:50:48,780
 ali većina kad se gleda,

1629
00:50:48,780 --> 00:50:49,460
 je sve slabija,

1630
00:50:49,460 --> 00:50:51,040
 slabija i slabija.

1631
00:50:51,320 --> 00:50:52,480
 To mora nekog da zustavi.

1632
00:50:52,480 --> 00:50:53,680
 A ne da kažem,

1633
00:50:53,680 --> 00:50:54,460
 ova generacija,

1634
00:50:54,460 --> 00:50:56,140
 X, Y, Z,

1635
00:50:56,140 --> 00:50:57,080
 to je specifična,

1636
00:50:57,080 --> 00:50:58,160
 dajte ljudi da vidimo

1637
00:50:58,160 --> 00:50:58,960
 šta se dešava.

1638
00:50:58,960 --> 00:51:00,260
 Okruženje se menja,

1639
00:51:00,260 --> 00:51:01,460
 menja se mozak nače dece.

1640
00:51:01,460 --> 00:51:03,600
 Iako mi ne budemo reagovali,

1641
00:51:03,600 --> 00:51:04,660
 pa neće niko.

1642
00:51:04,660 --> 00:51:06,460
 Eto, za to se založem.

1643
00:51:06,460 --> 00:51:07,600
 Da uradimo reformu,

1644
00:51:07,600 --> 00:51:08,840
 da krenemo malo zbilnije,

1645
00:51:08,840 --> 00:51:10,680
 da prihvatamo znači okruženje,

1646
00:51:10,680 --> 00:51:12,120
 neurofizijologiju,

1647
00:51:12,120 --> 00:51:13,060
 da bi pomogli.

1648
00:51:13,060 --> 00:51:16,600
 Ja pretpostavim da

1649
00:51:16,600 --> 00:51:19,420
 moju baku i djeda

1650
00:51:19,420 --> 00:51:21,400
 nitko nije educirao

1651
00:51:21,400 --> 00:51:22,900
 kako da budu bolji roditelji.

1652
00:51:22,900 --> 00:51:24,780
 Isto kao što mene danas

1653
00:51:24,780 --> 00:51:25,620
 nitko nije educirao

1654
00:51:25,620 --> 00:51:26,700
 da bi bio bolji roditelji.

1655
00:51:26,700 --> 00:51:27,000
 Znači,

1656
00:51:27,000 --> 00:51:29,320
 prepušteni smo bili sami sebi

1657
00:51:29,320 --> 00:51:32,360
 i u prije par generacije i danas.

1658
00:51:32,360 --> 00:51:34,020
 Da li ima jako važan faktor danas

1659
00:51:34,020 --> 00:51:34,840
 koji niko ne misli?

1660
00:51:34,840 --> 00:51:37,760
 Znači, baka i djeda,

1661
00:51:37,760 --> 00:51:39,080
 mama i tata nas puštaju,

1662
00:51:39,080 --> 00:51:39,640
 igramo se.

1663
00:51:39,640 --> 00:51:40,320
 S kim?

1664
00:51:40,320 --> 00:51:41,140
 S vršnjacima.

1665
00:51:41,140 --> 00:51:42,540
 Tu smo.

1666
00:51:42,540 --> 00:51:44,880
 Večera,

1667
00:51:44,880 --> 00:51:45,860
 mi dođemo.

1668
00:51:45,860 --> 00:51:47,000
 Ne dođemo,

1669
00:51:47,000 --> 00:51:47,340
 kažu,

1670
00:51:47,340 --> 00:51:48,700
 e, zovete baka,

1671
00:51:48,700 --> 00:51:49,360
 zovete mama.

1672
00:51:49,420 --> 00:51:49,920
 Znači,

1673
00:51:49,920 --> 00:51:50,380
 tu smo.

1674
00:51:50,380 --> 00:51:52,660
 Ali tu je okruženje

1675
00:51:52,660 --> 00:51:53,620
 bilo definisano.

1676
00:51:53,620 --> 00:51:54,100
 Mama,

1677
00:51:54,100 --> 00:51:54,540
 tata,

1678
00:51:54,540 --> 00:51:55,080
 baka,

1679
00:51:55,080 --> 00:51:55,920
 druga baka,

1680
00:51:55,920 --> 00:51:56,460
 prijatelje,

1681
00:51:56,460 --> 00:51:56,880
 to je to.

1682
00:51:56,880 --> 00:51:59,260
 Šta usmerava

1683
00:51:59,260 --> 00:52:00,980
 naše ponašanje?

1684
00:52:00,980 --> 00:52:02,260
 To je jako važno

1685
00:52:02,260 --> 00:52:02,920
 da svi shvate.

1686
00:52:02,920 --> 00:52:03,760
 Jer su naše dete

1687
00:52:03,760 --> 00:52:04,360
 u problemu,

1688
00:52:04,360 --> 00:52:05,340
 zarobljena su.

1689
00:52:05,340 --> 00:52:05,980
 Zašto?

1690
00:52:05,980 --> 00:52:07,720
 Pričali smo

1691
00:52:07,720 --> 00:52:08,920
 kada dete hoće da hodi

1692
00:52:08,920 --> 00:52:09,520
 kad prohoda,

1693
00:52:09,520 --> 00:52:10,440
 mi kažemo bravo.

1694
00:52:10,440 --> 00:52:11,760
 Znači,

1695
00:52:11,760 --> 00:52:12,560
 pohvala njima

1696
00:52:12,560 --> 00:52:13,660
 znači da su radili

1697
00:52:13,660 --> 00:52:14,420
 nešto dobro.

1698
00:52:14,420 --> 00:52:16,680
 Pa onda kad hoće

1699
00:52:16,680 --> 00:52:17,860
 da voze bicikl,

1700
00:52:18,740 --> 00:52:20,060
 nauče da voze bicikl.

1701
00:52:20,060 --> 00:52:20,700
 A muče se.

1702
00:52:20,700 --> 00:52:21,700
 Jedan dan,

1703
00:52:21,700 --> 00:52:22,260
 dva dana,

1704
00:52:22,260 --> 00:52:23,040
 pet metara,

1705
00:52:23,040 --> 00:52:23,460
 padnu,

1706
00:52:23,460 --> 00:52:24,080
 tri metara,

1707
00:52:24,080 --> 00:52:25,400
 držimo i odjednom,

1708
00:52:25,400 --> 00:52:25,860
 evo ga,

1709
00:52:25,860 --> 00:52:27,260
 dvadeset metara kreću.

1710
00:52:27,260 --> 00:52:28,660
 Većina dece stane.

1711
00:52:28,660 --> 00:52:29,400
 To je prilike

1712
00:52:29,400 --> 00:52:29,720
 četiri,

1713
00:52:29,720 --> 00:52:30,320
 pet godina.

1714
00:52:31,740 --> 00:52:32,640
 gledaju tatu,

1715
00:52:32,640 --> 00:52:32,960
 mamu,

1716
00:52:32,960 --> 00:52:33,700
 prolaznike,

1717
00:52:33,700 --> 00:52:35,140
 kao da hoće da kaže

1718
00:52:35,140 --> 00:52:36,240
 ja zna da voze bicikl.

1719
00:52:36,240 --> 00:52:37,560
 Možda i vrišta sreće.

1720
00:52:37,560 --> 00:52:39,780
 Uzumeju telefon svima da jave,

1721
00:52:39,780 --> 00:52:41,520
 možda baki,

1722
00:52:41,520 --> 00:52:43,160
 da zna da voze bicikl.

1723
00:52:43,160 --> 00:52:44,940
 Mozak je nučio nešto,

1724
00:52:44,940 --> 00:52:45,800
 no što je moza kaže,

1725
00:52:45,800 --> 00:52:46,440
 bravo,

1726
00:52:46,440 --> 00:52:47,520
 ovo je bilo teško

1727
00:52:47,520 --> 00:52:48,300
 i to se nučio.

1728
00:52:48,300 --> 00:52:49,400
 Oni su sresni.

1729
00:52:49,400 --> 00:52:50,940
 A šta rade mama i tata,

1730
00:52:50,940 --> 00:52:51,300
 bravo?

1731
00:52:51,300 --> 00:52:52,920
 Šta kaže baka,

1732
00:52:52,920 --> 00:52:53,380
 bravo?

1733
