01:22:18,780 --> 01:22:19,300
 evo pitanje

3091
01:22:19,300 --> 01:22:20,040
 za sve koje gledaju.

3092
01:22:20,040 --> 01:22:22,140
 A ko je životinje

3093
01:22:22,140 --> 01:22:23,380
 u reči mala,

3094
01:22:23,380 --> 01:22:25,120
 u rečenici mala vaza?

3095
01:22:25,120 --> 01:22:25,460
 I sad,

3096
01:22:25,460 --> 01:22:25,820
 naravno,

3097
01:22:25,900 --> 01:22:27,040
 to je već za starije

3098
01:22:27,040 --> 01:22:28,100
