3099
01:22:28,100 --> 01:22:29,460
 Mala vaza,

3100
01:22:29,460 --> 01:22:30,420
 kažu lav.

3101
01:22:30,420 --> 01:22:32,440
 E sad vi meni

3102
01:22:32,440 --> 01:22:33,500
 naprijete lav

3103
01:22:33,500 --> 01:22:34,800
 u dve susedne reči.

3104
01:22:34,800 --> 01:22:37,460
 Jedna reč zvrša na la,

3105
01:22:37,460 --> 01:22:38,500
