01:22:47,300 --> 01:22:49,540
 I to opet lav.

3111
01:22:49,540 --> 01:22:50,920
 Taj moment,

3112
01:22:50,920 --> 01:22:52,020
 kad su to radili,

3113
01:22:52,020 --> 01:22:52,680
 dobro to radim

3114
01:22:52,680 --> 01:22:53,340
 sa učiteljima

3115
01:22:53,340 --> 01:22:54,040
 na seminarima,

3116
01:22:54,040 --> 01:22:54,920
 taj moment,

3117
01:22:55,400 --> 01:22:56,640
 to se zove

3118
01:22:56,640 --> 01:22:58,160
 mislona klasifikacija,

3119
01:22:58,160 --> 01:22:59,520
 to je rana stimulacija.

3120
01:22:59,520 --> 01:23:00,640
 To ne može

3121
01:23:00,640 --> 01:23:01,340
 narod koji nema

3122
01:23:01,340 --> 01:23:02,140
