 dodamo iz našeg okruženja.

3153
01:23:42,120 --> 01:23:42,980
 To ću sad raditi

3154
01:23:42,980 --> 01:23:44,680
 na učiteljskom fakultetu

3155
01:23:44,680 --> 01:23:45,160
 u Zagrebu.

3156
01:23:45,160 --> 01:23:46,480
 Dajte da mi vidimo

3157
01:23:46,480 --> 01:23:47,460
 kako mozak radi,

3158
01:23:47,460 --> 01:23:48,700
 kako se aktiviraju

3159
01:23:48,700 --> 01:23:49,260
 te regije.

3160
01:23:49,260 --> 01:23:50,440
 Dajte da uzmemo teorije

3161
01:23:50,440 --> 01:23:51,520
 koje postoje pa da dodamo

3162
01:23:51,520 --> 01:23:52,800
 nešto iz našeg okruženja.

3163
01:23:52,800 --> 01:23:54,180
 Jer ako budemo koristili

3164
01:23:54,180 --> 01:23:55,260
 tuzje teorije

3165
01:23:55,260 --> 01:23:56,300
 bez ikakve promjene,

3166
01:23:56,800 --> 01:23:58,200
 nema tu naprijed.

3167
01:23:58,200 --> 01:23:59,320
 Promjenilo se okruženje.

3168
01:23:59,320 --> 01:24:00,600
 Mora brže da se radi.

3169
01:24:00,600 --> 01:24:03,040
 A što je

3170
01:24:03,040 --> 01:24:04,240
 od svega ovoga

3171
01:24:04,240 --> 01:24:05,180
 što ste rekli do sada,

3172
01:24:05,180 --> 01:24:06,340
 što je primjenjivo

3173
01:24:06,340 --> 01:24:07,000
 za roditelje?

3174
01:24:07,000 --> 01:24:08,280
 To je što je primjenjivo

3175
01:24:08,280 --> 01:24:09,180
 za odrasle?

3176
01:24:09,180 --> 01:24:10,600
 Evo roditelj odmah.

3177
01:24:10,600 --> 01:24:11,400
 Posljedan da ovo sve

3178
01:24:11,400 --> 01:24:12,460
 primjenjivo je na odrasle.

3179
01:24:12,460 --> 01:24:12,820
 Pre zaštisivanje.

3180
01:24:12,820 --> 01:24:13,220
 Tako je.

3181
01:24:13,220 --> 01:24:14,340
 Pre zaštisivanje je grešo.

3182
01:24:14,340 --> 01:24:15,320
 Mislim od ove igre

3183
01:24:15,320 --> 01:24:16,340
 od kreativnosti.

3184
01:24:16,340 --> 01:24:16,360
 Odmah ću reći.

3185
01:24:16,360 --> 01:24:17,640
 Idemo sad da je od rođenja

3186
01:24:17,640 --> 01:24:19,320
 do trece, do pete za roditelje

3187
01:24:19,320 --> 01:24:21,220
 pre zaštisivanje je štetno.

3188
01:24:21,220 --> 01:24:23,380
 Pustite dete da padne,

3189
01:24:23,380 --> 01:24:24,500
 ali ne na betonu,

3190
01:24:24,500 --> 01:24:25,100
 na livadi,

3191
01:24:25,100 --> 01:24:26,720
 pa na dve ruke,

3192
01:24:26,720 --> 01:24:27,360
 pa na jednu,

3193
01:24:27,360 --> 01:24:28,000
 pa na lakat,

3194
01:24:28,000 --> 01:24:28,900
 neka padne.

3195
01:24:28,900 --> 01:24:30,460
 Pustite kada se vrti.

3196
01:24:30,460 --> 01:24:31,840
 Ne po stepenicama,

3197
01:24:31,840 --> 01:24:33,220
 nego po parketu,

3198
01:24:33,220 --> 01:24:33,800
 po tepihu,

3199
01:24:33,800 --> 01:24:34,380
 na livadi.

3200
01:24:34,380 --> 01:24:36,220
 Znači dete mora da se vrti,

3201
01:24:36,220 --> 01:24:36,800
 da skače,

3202
01:24:36,800 --> 01:24:37,600
 da se kreće.

3203
01:24:37,600 --> 01:24:40,200
 Pre zaštisivanje

3204
01:24:40,200 --> 01:24:41,220
 ošteće dete.

3205
01:24:41,220 --> 01:24:42,000
 Znači nema one

3206
01:24:42,000 --> 01:24:42,820
 pazi pašćiš.

3207
01:24:42,820 --> 01:24:44,540
 Pa može,

3208
01:24:44,540 --> 01:24:45,740
 ako je po stepenicama

3209
01:24:45,740 --> 01:24:46,840
 se zatrčalo dete,

3210
01:24:47,000 --> 01:24:48,420
 a moramo da ga vodimo

3211
01:24:48,420 --> 01:24:49,780
 da je prirodno park.

3212
01:24:49,780 --> 01:24:51,020
 Je li tako?

3213
01:24:51,020 --> 01:24:51,460
 Livada.

3214
01:24:51,460 --> 01:24:53,240
 Tu neka padne.

3215
01:24:53,240 --> 01:24:54,140
 Onda dalje.

3216
01:24:54,140 --> 01:24:55,280
 Idemo,

3217
01:24:55,280 --> 01:24:57,180
 rana stimulacija kognitivna,

3218
01:24:57,180 --> 01:24:58,740
 da aktiviram asocijtene regije,

3219
01:24:58,740 --> 01:24:59,600
 nelogične priječe,

3220
01:24:59,600 --> 01:25:00,520
 čitajte im bajke.

3221
01:25:00,520 --> 01:25:02,620
 Izmislite bajku.

3222
01:25:02,620 --> 01:25:04,340
 Kako?

3223
01:25:04,340 --> 01:25:05,600
 Pa izmislite bajku.

3224
01:25:05,600 --> 01:25:06,500
 U prijativo.

3225
01:25:06,500 --> 01:25:07,620
 Izmislite ću u školi

3226
01:25:07,620 --> 01:25:08,960
 i u Andrići Zagreba.

3227
01:25:08,960 --> 01:25:11,120
 Znači dajte im nelogične priječe,

3228
01:25:11,120 --> 01:25:12,080
 izmislite bajku,

3229
01:25:12,080 --> 01:25:13,020
 pričite bajke,

3230
01:25:13,020 --> 01:25:14,680
 dajte im sakrivanje reči.

3231
01:25:14,680 --> 01:25:16,100
 Kompas pas.

3232
01:25:16,780 --> 01:25:17,720
 To je najlakši nivo.

3233
01:25:17,720 --> 01:25:19,220
 Koji životinju reči?

3234
01:25:19,220 --> 01:25:20,080
 Kompas pas.

3235
01:25:20,080 --> 01:25:21,260
 A što je malo teže?

3236
01:25:21,260 --> 01:25:22,800
 Već za prvi i drugi razred.

3237
01:25:22,800 --> 01:25:24,080
 Ovo je bilo za vrtiće.

3238
01:25:24,080 --> 01:25:25,020
 A za prvi i drugi,

3239
01:25:25,020 --> 01:25:29,020
 koji čovekov prijatelj

3240
01:25:29,020 --> 01:25:30,560
 se nalazi u reči kompas?

3241
01:25:30,560 --> 01:25:32,720
 Pas.

3242
01:25:32,720 --> 01:25:34,520
 A još teže pitanje

3243
01:25:34,520 --> 01:25:35,480
 za drugi i treći razred.

3244
01:25:35,480 --> 01:25:37,240
 Koji čovekov prijatelj

3245
01:25:37,240 --> 01:25:38,300
 se nalazi u nečemu

3246
01:25:38,300 --> 01:25:39,060
 što nam pomože

3247
01:25:39,060 --> 01:25:40,060
 za orijentaciju?

3248
01:25:41,360 --> 01:25:43,180
 To su mislni procesi.

3249
01:25:43,180 --> 01:25:44,440
 Orientacija,

3250
01:25:44,440 --> 01:25:45,000
 kompas,

3251
01:25:45,000 --> 01:25:45,440
 prijatelj,

3252
01:25:45,440 --> 01:25:45,740
 pas,

3253
01:25:45,740 --> 01:25:46,100
 kompas,

3254
01:25:46,100 --> 01:25:46,360
 pas.

3255
01:25:46,360 --> 01:25:47,740
 Znači isto je pitanje

3256
01:25:47,740 --> 01:25:49,160
 za vrtić za školu

3257
01:25:49,160 --> 01:25:50,120
 i za peti razred.

3258
01:25:50,120 --> 01:25:51,600
 Što je meni cilj?

3259
01:25:51,600 --> 01:25:52,440
 Rekao sam,

3260
01:25:52,440 --> 01:25:54,100
 doni mene naprave pitanje.

3261
01:25:54,100 --> 01:25:55,420
 I oni tada koriste

3262
01:25:55,420 --> 01:25:56,340
 školskog rade,

3263
01:25:56,340 --> 01:25:57,020
 uzimaju,

3264
01:25:57,020 --> 01:25:58,320
 prave mi pitanje,

3265
01:25:58,320 --> 01:25:59,040
 što su radili,

3266
01:25:59,040 --> 01:26:00,440
 ponučili su lekciju,

3267
01:26:00,440 --> 01:26:01,060
 ključne reči,

3268
01:26:01,060 --> 01:26:01,820
 još su i mislili.

3269
01:26:02,820 --> 01:26:03,520
 A što je suprotno?

3270
01:26:03,520 --> 01:26:05,140
 Duče na pameti da zaboravi.

3271
01:26:05,140 --> 01:26:07,200
 Znači to je za roditelje

3272
01:26:07,200 --> 01:26:08,400
 nelogične priječe

3273
01:26:08,400 --> 01:26:09,240
 sa krivanje reči

3274
01:26:09,240 --> 01:26:10,220
 onda dolazi škola.

3275
01:26:10,220 --> 01:26:12,640
 Onda moramo gradivo

3276
01:26:12,640 --> 01:26:15,160
 da stavljamo funkciju

3277
01:26:15,160 --> 01:26:15,740
 razmiješljenja

3278
01:26:15,740 --> 01:26:16,720
 kao što su vijalvatros.

3279
01:26:16,720 --> 01:26:18,240
 Da oni misle

3280
01:26:18,240 --> 01:26:19,500
 i oni naučaju puno toga.

3281
01:26:19,500 --> 01:26:20,440
 Kaže neko,

3282
01:26:20,440 --> 01:26:22,520
 a kako onda nauče matematiku

3283
01:26:22,520 --> 01:26:23,060
 i to može,

3284
