3318
01:27:15,840 --> 01:27:17,400
 I tada nam kažu,

3319
01:27:17,400 --> 01:27:18,300
 ja sam bio u šoku,

3320
01:27:18,300 --> 01:27:20,440
 da oni imaju metode

3321
01:27:20,440 --> 01:27:22,160
 učenja vikanjem.

3322
01:27:23,600 --> 01:27:24,040
