3323
01:27:24,040 --> 01:27:24,440
 Da.

3324
01:27:24,440 --> 01:27:26,140
 Pa kako?

3325
01:27:26,140 --> 01:27:28,240
 Pa primetili su kad učitelj

3326
01:27:28,240 --> 01:27:29,760
 vikne da deto upamti.

3327
01:27:29,760 --> 01:27:31,340
 Pa su onda razvili

3328
01:27:31,340 --> 01:27:32,120
 celu metodu

3329
01:27:32,120 --> 01:27:34,600
 kako viće sa raširanim rukama,

3330
01:27:34,600 --> 01:27:35,860
 po dijagonali,

3331
01:27:35,860 --> 01:27:36,740
 ispred deteta,

3332
01:27:36,740 --> 01:27:37,560
 u polu,

3333
01:27:37,560 --> 01:27:37,940
 u čučnju,

3334
01:27:37,940 --> 01:27:39,200
 gledamo dete u rame,

3335
01:27:39,200 --> 01:27:40,060
 u lakat, u oči.

3336
01:27:40,060 --> 01:27:41,280
 Ja njih slušam

3337
01:27:41,280 --> 01:27:43,200
 i pitam,

3338
01:27:43,200 --> 01:27:45,040
 pa znate koja je funkcija

3339
01:27:45,040 --> 01:27:46,220
 vikanja u fiziologiji?

3340
01:27:46,220 --> 01:27:48,980
 Pa kao ne?

3341
01:27:48,980 --> 01:27:50,580
 I ovo je za roditelje.

3342
01:27:50,580 --> 01:27:52,200
 I još jedan savet.

