01:27:52,200 --> 01:27:54,700
 Nemojte vikati na dete.

3344
01:27:54,700 --> 01:27:55,080
 Zašto?

3345
01:27:55,080 --> 01:27:57,200
 Vikanje služi za mozak.

3346
01:27:57,200 --> 01:27:58,940
 Da ga zustavimo.

3347
01:27:58,940 --> 01:28:00,220
 Jer mozak je organ

3348
01:28:00,220 --> 01:28:01,740
 za preživljavanje.

3349
01:28:01,740 --> 01:28:03,200
 Dete hoda,

3350
01:28:03,200 --> 01:28:04,080
 ivicom provali,

3351
01:28:04,080 --> 01:28:05,200
 stani, on stane.

3352
01:28:05,200 --> 01:28:06,680
 Hoda po tankom ledu,

3353
01:28:06,680 --> 01:28:07,780
 stani, dete stane.

3354
01:28:07,780 --> 01:28:08,980
 Trči po parkingu,

3355
01:28:08,980 --> 01:28:10,140
 stane, dete stane.

