01:33:46,300 --> 01:33:47,180
 nemaju neurone

3633
01:33:47,180 --> 01:33:48,500
 koje ima neurone

3634
01:33:48,500 --> 01:33:49,100
 pa žive biće

3635
01:33:49,100 --> 01:33:49,860
 koje se kreću.

3636
01:33:49,860 --> 01:33:51,200
 Znači kretanje

3637
01:33:51,200 --> 01:33:52,740
 formira nervne puteve.

3638
01:33:52,740 --> 01:33:54,760
 Iako nemaju skok nazad,

3639
01:33:54,760 --> 01:33:55,440
 bočni skok,

3640
01:33:55,440 --> 01:33:57,120
 mi imamo kognitivne probleme.

3641
01:33:57,120 --> 01:33:59,680
 Zato je jako važno kretanje.

3642
01:33:59,680 --> 01:34:01,900
 Sviranje instrumenta

3643
01:34:01,900 --> 01:34:02,580
 sa prstićima

3644
01:34:02,580 --> 01:34:03,460
 da vide neke note

3645
01:34:03,460 --> 01:34:04,120
 da sviraju.

3646
01:34:04,120 --> 01:34:05,740
 Radio sam prvo

3647
01:34:05,740 --> 01:34:06,600
 kad su UNICEF-om

3648
01:34:06,600 --> 01:34:07,500
 pa smo nučili

3649
01:34:07,500 --> 01:34:08,480
 u decu vrtiću

3650
01:34:08,480 --> 01:34:09,540
 za dva sata

3651
01:34:09,540 --> 01:34:10,140
 kroz igru

3652
01:34:10,140 --> 01:34:11,940
 da prepoznaju note

3653
01:34:11,940 --> 01:34:12,940
 i jednom rukom

3654
01:34:12,940 --> 01:34:13,520
 da sviraju.

3655
01:34:13,520 --> 01:34:14,260
 Znači može,

3656
01:34:14,260 --> 01:34:15,120
 ali da liče na igru.

3657
01:34:15,120 --> 01:34:15,980
 A kako se uči

3658
01:34:15,980 --> 01:34:16,900
 kod nas regularno?

3659
01:34:16,900 --> 01:34:18,020
 Treći razred

3660
01:34:18,020 --> 01:34:19,000
 idemo nota do,

3661
01:34:19,000 --> 01:34:20,500
 gde se nalazi nota do,

3662
01:34:20,500 --> 01:34:21,680
 to je učenje na pamet.

3663
01:34:21,680 --> 01:34:22,920
 Moramo metode

3664
01:34:22,920 --> 01:34:23,480
 da menjamo.

3665
01:34:23,480 --> 01:34:24,640
 A zašto likovno?

3666
01:34:24,640 --> 01:34:26,300
 Pono što su zamislili

3667
01:34:26,300 --> 01:34:27,140
 da prstićima

3668
01:34:27,140 --> 01:34:28,260
 prebace na papir.

3669
01:34:28,260 --> 01:34:30,420
 Znači meni je kretanje

3670
01:34:30,420 --> 01:34:31,100
 čak osno

3671
01:34:31,100 --> 01:34:32,920
 i zamislene kognitivne procese.

3672
01:34:32,920 --> 01:34:34,300
 Znači prvo je kretanje

3673
01:34:34,300 --> 01:34:35,280
 pa onda matematika.

3674
01:34:35,280 --> 01:34:37,780
 Tu se puno greši.

3675
01:34:37,780 --> 01:34:39,540
 Pričam ja sa koleginicam,

3676
01:34:39,540 --> 01:34:40,480
 one ne mogu da stignu

3677
01:34:40,480 --> 01:34:41,220
 recimo gradi

3678
01:34:41,220 --> 01:34:41,960
 uz matematike,

3679
01:34:41,960 --> 01:34:42,360
 pa onda,

3680
01:34:42,360 --> 01:34:44,140
 ako su bili nevjeni,

3681
01:34:44,140 --> 01:34:45,500
 e, sad ćemo raditi

3682
01:34:45,500 --> 01:34:46,340
 matematiku,

3683
01:34:46,340 --> 01:34:47,600
 a ne fizičko,

3684
01:34:47,600 --> 01:34:48,360
 to je stjelesni.

3685
01:34:49,020 --> 01:34:50,180
 Kado smo je mnogo ocekli?

3686
01:34:50,180 --> 01:34:51,440
 I evo save za kraj,

3687
01:34:51,440 --> 01:34:52,100
 učitelji.

3688
01:34:52,100 --> 01:34:54,180
 Mi imamo jako puno kretanje

3689
01:34:54,180 --> 01:34:54,740
 u čionici.

3690
01:34:54,740 --> 01:34:56,640
 Nemamo svaki dan

3691
01:34:56,640 --> 01:34:58,060
 tjelesni fizičko,

3692
01:34:58,060 --> 01:34:58,480
 nema.

3693
01:34:58,480 --> 01:34:59,600
 Što onda radimo?

3694
01:34:59,600 --> 01:35:01,680
 Razapnemo između klupa,

3695
01:35:01,680 --> 01:35:02,200
 lastišu,

3696
01:35:02,200 --> 01:35:02,980
 visinu kolena.

3697
01:35:02,980 --> 01:35:04,400
 Okočimo male zvončiće.

3698
01:35:04,400 --> 01:35:06,500
 I kad idu nešto napišu,

3699
01:35:06,500 --> 01:35:07,240
 idu preko toga,

3700
01:35:07,240 --> 01:35:07,840
 napišu,

3701
01:35:07,840 --> 01:35:09,120
 i unazad na mesto.

3702
01:35:09,120 --> 01:35:09,780
 Šta smo dobili,

3703
01:35:09,780 --> 01:35:10,400
 koji fenomen?

3704
01:35:10,400 --> 01:35:11,980
 Svi se javljaju.

3705
01:35:11,980 --> 01:35:13,080
 Ne da bi pisali,

3706
01:35:13,080 --> 01:35:14,320
 pa da bi se kretali.

3707
01:35:14,320 --> 01:35:15,080
 Pa sam dobio

3708
01:35:15,080 --> 01:35:15,840
 mislani proces.

3709
01:35:19,020 --> 01:35:20,360
 Žuta, crvena, žuta, crvena.

3710
01:35:20,360 --> 01:35:21,660
 Kada dođe na žutu,

3711
01:35:21,660 --> 01:35:23,300
 kažu limun,

3712
01:35:23,300 --> 01:35:25,980
 na crvenu trešnje ili višnje.

3713
01:35:25,980 --> 01:35:27,360
 Ili žuta je glagol,

3714
01:35:27,360 --> 01:35:28,480
 crvena je imenica.

3715
01:35:28,480 --> 01:35:29,780
 Ili žuta je parni,

3716
01:35:29,780 --> 01:35:31,460
 crvena je neparni broj.

3717
01:35:31,460 --> 01:35:32,720
 Oni ponavljaju,

3718
01:35:32,720 --> 01:35:33,860
 gradiju dok se kreću.

3719
01:35:33,860 --> 01:35:37,820
 To je prava struktura mozga

3720
01:35:37,820 --> 01:35:38,800
 da sve popamti

3721
01:35:38,800 --> 01:35:41,240
 u kretanju da mislimo,

3722
01:35:41,240 --> 01:35:42,580
 a ne da sedimo i da slušamo.

3723
01:35:42,580 --> 01:35:43,460
 Može to,

3724
01:35:43,460 --> 01:35:44,680
 ali bolje da se kreću.

3725
01:35:44,680 --> 01:35:46,540
 Tako da upunimo tih savjeta

3726
01:35:46,540 --> 01:35:47,620
 malo je vremena,

3727
01:35:47,680 --> 01:35:49,340
 mislim da smo dosta toga dotakli

3728
01:35:49,340 --> 01:35:51,120
 da pomognemo i učiteljima

3729
01:35:51,120 --> 01:35:53,100
 i roditeljima da nešto promene.

3730
01:35:53,100 --> 01:35:54,660
 Dajte vi meni recite

3731
01:35:54,660 --> 01:35:57,920
 zašto se vaša organizacija

3732
01:35:57,920 --> 01:35:58,740
 zove NTC,

3733
01:35:58,740 --> 01:36:00,760
 to je Nikola Tesla centar.

3734
01:36:00,760 --> 01:36:03,380
 Odakle je inspiracija

3735
01:36:03,380 --> 01:36:04,560
 tada se zove baš tako.

3736
01:36:04,560 --> 01:36:07,000
 Pa ja sam osnivač

3737
01:36:07,000 --> 01:36:07,860
 mese u Srbiji,

3738
01:36:07,860 --> 01:36:09,000
 Sloveniji, Crnogori.

3739
01:36:09,000 --> 01:36:10,440
 Pomogu sam puno u Hrvatskoj.

3740
01:36:10,440 --> 01:36:12,540
 I onda sam vidio

3741
01:36:12,540 --> 01:36:12,900
 da u mese

3742
01:36:12,900 --> 01:36:14,560
 nema baš puno darovitih.

3743
01:36:14,560 --> 01:36:16,360
 Ja sam se tu iznenadio.

3744
01:36:17,300 --> 01:36:18,020
 Znači u mese ima

3745
01:36:18,020 --> 01:36:19,060
 15% darovitih,

3746
01:36:19,060 --> 01:36:19,740
 što je ipak više

3747
01:36:19,740 --> 01:36:21,400
 nego opšto u populaciji

3748
01:36:21,400 --> 01:36:22,100
 gdje je 2%.

3749
01:36:22,100 --> 01:36:22,680
 Mi smo napili

3750
01:36:22,680 --> 01:36:24,160
 oceg kao za darovite

3751
01:36:24,160 --> 01:36:25,840
 Nikola Tesla centar.

3752
01:36:25,840 --> 01:36:28,300
 Onda sam ja tu razvio

3753
01:36:28,300 --> 01:36:28,840
 programe

3754
01:36:28,840 --> 01:36:29,780
 kako da radimo.

3755
01:36:29,780 --> 01:36:30,280
 Onda sam vidio

3756
01:36:30,280 --> 01:36:31,080
 da ti programe

3757
01:36:31,080 --> 01:36:32,280
 nisu samo za darovite,

3758
01:36:32,280 --> 01:36:32,620
 mogu

3759
01:36:32,620 --> 01:36:33,700
 svakom učeniku

3760
01:36:33,700 --> 01:36:34,320
 da pomognu.

3761
01:36:34,320 --> 01:36:36,280
 I onda sam radio

3762
01:36:36,280 --> 01:36:37,220
 neki evo projekat

3763
01:36:37,220 --> 01:36:38,820
 kao Nikola Tesla centar

3764
01:36:38,820 --> 01:36:39,240
 pa su rekli

3765
01:36:39,240 --> 01:36:40,220
 ne možete vi koristiti

3766
01:36:40,220 --> 01:36:41,780
 Nikola Tesla ime tek tako.

3767
01:36:41,780 --> 01:36:43,100
 Pa sam prijavio projekat

3768
01:36:43,100 --> 01:36:44,060
 samo kao NTC

3769
01:36:44,060 --> 01:36:45,540
 tako da je ostala NTC.

3770
01:36:45,540 --> 01:36:47,960
 A počela kao Nikola Tesla centar

3771
01:36:47,960 --> 01:36:49,480
 a sad je samo NTC.

3772
01:36:49,480 --> 01:36:50,960
 Što vas inspirira

3773
01:36:50,960 --> 01:36:51,420
 ko Tesla?

3774
01:36:51,420 --> 01:36:54,420
 Pa i tu sam izučavao

3775
01:36:54,420 --> 01:36:55,260
 njegov spavanje.

3776
01:36:55,260 --> 01:36:56,020
 Ne znam da li znate

3777
01:36:56,020 --> 01:36:57,560
 on je jako malo spavao.

3778
01:36:59,140 --> 01:37:00,240
 On je toliko malo spavao

3779
01:37:00,240 --> 01:37:01,740
 da bi sad po nekim merilima

3780
01:37:01,740 --> 01:37:03,960
 on moro da ima

3781
01:37:03,960 --> 01:37:05,660
 neki izdravstveni problem.

3782
01:37:05,660 --> 01:37:06,580
 On je bilo zdrav.

3783
01:37:06,580 --> 01:37:08,920
 Ali što on u stvari radio?

3784
01:37:08,920 --> 01:37:11,300
 On je poznat po tome

3785
01:37:11,300 --> 01:37:13,080
 što je radio vizualizaciju.

3786
01:37:13,080 --> 01:37:14,820
 On naprije neku mašinu

3787
01:37:14,820 --> 01:37:15,800
 pa stavi u misli.

3788
01:37:15,800 --> 01:37:16,900
 Pa je pokreće.

3789
01:37:16,900 --> 01:37:18,660
 Pa je popravlju u mislima.

3790
01:37:18,660 --> 01:37:21,220
 I njegovih prototipi

3791
01:37:21,220 --> 01:37:22,820
 su radili skoro iz prve.

3792
01:37:22,820 --> 01:37:24,260
 Dok drugi neki

3793
01:37:24,260 --> 01:37:25,380
 recimo Edison

3794
01:37:25,380 --> 01:37:26,880
 on uradi jednu mašinu

3795
01:37:26,880 --> 01:37:27,420
 pa ne valja

3796
01:37:27,420 --> 01:37:28,800
 pa drugu, pa treću, pa petu

3797
01:37:28,800 --> 01:37:29,920
 pa ne valja to, pa šestu.

3798
01:37:29,920 --> 01:37:30,880
 To je jako skupo.

3799
01:37:30,880 --> 01:37:32,440
 Tesla je radio glavi.

3800
01:37:32,440 --> 01:37:34,400
 I ta sposobnost

3801
01:37:34,400 --> 01:37:35,360
 kad neko to radi

3802
01:37:35,360 --> 01:37:36,620
 što u stvari aktivira?

3803
01:37:36,620 --> 01:37:37,540
 Pa ceo mozak.

3804
01:37:37,540 --> 01:37:40,560
 A ceo mozak kad radi

3805
01:37:40,560 --> 01:37:41,960
 sinkrona moždana aktivnost

3806
01:37:41,960 --> 01:37:43,600
 to malo liči

3807
01:37:43,600 --> 01:37:44,760
 na remfazu spavanja.

3808
01:37:44,760 --> 01:37:47,180
 Sad meni žao nije živ

3809
01:37:47,180 --> 01:37:49,360
 ali velike ti naočnici

3810
01:37:49,360 --> 01:37:50,760
 su malo spavili

3811
01:37:50,760 --> 01:37:52,160
 kao da on obavije remfazu

3812
01:37:52,160 --> 01:37:53,020
 dok je budan

3813
01:37:53,020 --> 01:37:55,100
 kao da sanje otvorenih očiju

3814
01:37:55,100 --> 01:37:55,940
 jer mozak radi

3815
01:37:55,940 --> 01:37:57,220
 u tom fokusu

3816
01:37:57,220 --> 01:37:58,960
 kao remfazi

3817
01:37:58,960 --> 01:38:00,760
 mislim nije kao li blizu

3818
01:38:00,760 --> 01:38:01,320
 slično je.

3819
01:38:01,320 --> 01:38:03,220
 Moguće da njemu

3820
01:38:03,220 --> 01:38:03,980
 toliko noći

3821
01:38:03,980 --> 01:38:05,860
 remfaza ne bila ni potrebna.

3822
01:38:05,860 --> 01:38:06,840
 On je nju odradio

3823
01:38:06,840 --> 01:38:07,460
 po danu

3824
01:38:07,460 --> 01:38:08,800
 jer mi moramo da imamo

3825
01:38:08,800 --> 01:38:09,440
 remfazu.

3826
01:38:09,440 --> 01:38:11,460
 Mi kad legnemo da spavamo

3827
01:38:11,460 --> 01:38:13,560
 remfaza na sati i po vremena

3828
01:38:13,560 --> 01:38:15,680
 i to je to.

3829
01:38:15,680 --> 01:38:17,040
 On to nije imao

3830
01:38:17,040 --> 01:38:18,520
 ako je spavao samo dva sata.

3831
01:38:18,520 --> 01:38:20,740
 Kako je mogo da žive?

3832
01:38:20,740 --> 01:38:21,800
 Znači imamo odgovor

3833
01:38:21,800 --> 01:38:22,660
 da možda njegov mozak

3834
01:38:22,660 --> 01:38:23,560
 to odradzivao

3835
01:38:23,560 --> 01:38:25,480
 dok je bio budan.

3836
01:38:25,480 --> 01:38:27,380
 I to je meni fascinant

3837
01:38:27,380 --> 01:38:28,680
 on je imao neki rad mozga

3838
01:38:28,680 --> 01:38:29,500
 koji mi nemamo

3839
01:38:29,500 --> 01:38:31,160
 koji medicina ne poznaje.

3840
01:38:31,160 --> 01:38:32,940
 Znači pak je bio drugačiji

3841
01:38:32,940 --> 01:38:33,840
 i to ne malo

3842
01:38:33,840 --> 01:38:35,180
 nego puno puno.

3843
01:38:35,180 --> 01:38:36,300
 Pa se imamo priliku

3844
01:38:36,300 --> 01:38:37,280
 za remfazu

3845
01:38:37,280 --> 01:38:37,920
 sam tu izučao

3846
01:38:37,920 --> 01:38:39,020
 zbog mog mangestarskog.

3847
01:38:39,020 --> 01:38:40,460
 Imao sam priliku

3848
01:38:40,460 --> 01:38:41,400
 sa Karpovom

3849
01:38:41,400 --> 01:38:41,880
 da budem

3850
01:38:41,880 --> 01:38:43,140
 dve godine

3851
01:38:43,140 --> 01:38:43,840
 po sedam dane

3852
01:38:43,840 --> 01:38:44,720
 bio na ovom sadu.

3853
01:38:44,720 --> 01:38:46,440
 Bili smo u organizaciji

3854
01:38:46,440 --> 01:38:47,380
 turnira

3855
01:38:47,380 --> 01:38:48,700
 Šakovsku olimpijada

3856
01:38:48,700 --> 01:38:49,960
 za decu

3857
01:38:49,960 --> 01:38:50,820
 do 16 godina.

3858
01:38:50,820 --> 01:38:51,300
 Kasparov?

3859
01:38:51,300 --> 01:38:52,140
 Karpov.

3860
01:38:52,140 --> 01:38:52,700
 Karpov.

3861
01:38:52,700 --> 01:38:53,860
 On je bio prvog

3862
01:38:53,860 --> 01:38:54,700
