3863
01:38:54,700 --> 01:38:56,460
 I sad vi kad ste s nekim

3864
01:38:56,460 --> 01:38:57,820
 nekoliko dana

3865
01:38:57,820 --> 01:38:58,740
 doručak, ručak

3866
01:38:58,740 --> 01:38:59,200
 pa sedimo

3867
01:38:59,200 --> 01:38:59,700
 dvati sada

3868
01:38:59,700 --> 01:39:00,400
 pričamo stvarno

3869
01:39:00,400 --> 01:39:01,020
 sve i svašta.

3870
01:39:01,020 --> 01:39:02,340
 Ja njega pitam

3871
01:39:02,340 --> 01:39:03,400
 znajući

3872
01:39:03,400 --> 01:39:05,060
 da u remfazu

3873
01:39:05,060 --> 01:39:06,000
 prolađen recimo

3874
01:39:06,000 --> 01:39:06,780
 periodni sistem

3875
01:39:06,780 --> 01:39:07,460
 elemenata.

3876
01:39:07,460 --> 01:39:09,000
 Mendeljev je čak

3877
01:39:09,000 --> 01:39:10,180
 govorio da je sanjao

3878
01:39:10,180 --> 01:39:11,600
 da su svi elementi

3879
01:39:11,600 --> 01:39:12,560
 došli na svoje mesto

3880
01:39:12,560 --> 01:39:13,440
 samo jedan posle

3881
01:39:13,440 --> 01:39:14,240
 morao da popravi.

3882
01:39:14,240 --> 01:39:15,820
 I sad je pitanje

3883
01:39:15,820 --> 01:39:16,280
 kako je to

3884
01:39:16,280 --> 01:39:17,300
 Mendeljev sanjao

3885
01:39:17,300 --> 01:39:18,780
 najveće otkrijeće

3886
01:39:18,780 --> 01:39:19,780
 iz fizike i hemije.

3887
01:39:19,780 --> 01:39:20,720
 Sanjao.

3888
01:39:20,720 --> 01:39:21,780
 Što nas dvojca

3889
01:39:21,780 --> 01:39:22,540
 nismo sanjali?

3890
01:39:22,540 --> 01:39:23,720
 Evo što ljudi

