 Nacrtao je srce,

4176
01:45:07,980 --> 01:45:09,860
 a preko srca

4177
01:45:09,860 --> 01:45:10,620
 Hanzaplast.

4178
01:45:10,620 --> 01:45:12,560
 To je to.

4179
01:45:12,560 --> 01:45:13,940
 I ja sam njemu

4180
01:45:13,940 --> 01:45:14,980
 istraživo, ispitivo.

4181
01:45:14,980 --> 01:45:16,680
 Ja tu njegu pesmicu

4182
01:45:16,680 --> 01:45:17,820
 dan danas pokazujem

4183
01:45:17,820 --> 01:45:18,920
 na svim seminarima

4184
01:45:18,920 --> 01:45:20,600
 od Amerike do Australije.

4185
01:45:20,820 --> 01:45:21,500
 da pokazujem

4186
01:45:21,500 --> 01:45:22,840
 šta je slikovno pizmo,

4187
01:45:22,840 --> 01:45:24,440
 a šta je asocijativno.

4188
01:45:24,440 --> 01:45:24,780
 Znači,

4189
01:45:24,780 --> 01:45:26,080
 ima i korak dalje.

4190
01:45:26,080 --> 01:45:26,860
 Asocijativno,

4191
01:45:26,860 --> 01:45:27,260
 zašto?

4192
01:45:27,260 --> 01:45:29,120
 Jer vid služi,

4193
01:45:29,120 --> 01:45:30,800
 to je naše čulo,

4194
01:45:30,800 --> 01:45:31,600
 naše osjetilo.

4195
01:45:31,600 --> 01:45:32,400
 Da vidimo,

4196
01:45:32,400 --> 01:45:32,800
 recimo,

4197
01:45:32,800 --> 01:45:33,700
 vidimo dim.

4198
01:45:33,700 --> 01:45:35,160
 Šta kaže mozog?

4199
01:45:35,160 --> 01:45:35,920
 Idi gasi vatru

4200
01:45:35,920 --> 01:45:36,860
 ili idi beži.

4201
01:45:36,860 --> 01:45:37,880
 Koja funkcija dima?

4202
01:45:37,880 --> 01:45:39,420
 Pa da napravi asocijaciju.

4203
01:45:39,420 --> 01:45:39,780
 Znači,

4204
01:45:39,780 --> 01:45:40,560
 koja funkcija slike?

4205
01:45:40,560 --> 01:45:43,480
 Pa da napravi asocijaciju.

4206
01:45:43,480 --> 01:45:44,120
 Znači,

4207
01:45:44,120 --> 01:45:45,120
 mi moramo da idemo

4208
01:45:45,120 --> 01:45:46,920
 ne sa teksta na sliku,

4209
01:45:46,920 --> 01:45:48,240
 nego moramo sa teksta

4210
01:45:48,240 --> 01:45:49,760
 na asocijaciju.

4211
01:45:49,760 --> 01:45:51,740
 Pa na paralelnu asocijaciju,

4212
01:45:51,740 --> 01:45:52,680
 pa na analogičnu,

4213
01:45:52,680 --> 01:45:54,180
 tada se mozak budi.

4214
01:45:54,180 --> 01:45:57,360
 To je neki put za reformu

4215
01:45:57,360 --> 01:45:58,500
 iz mog predmeta

4216
01:45:58,500 --> 01:45:59,700
 koju je predna na fakultetu.

4217
01:45:59,700 --> 01:46:02,300
 Nadam se da će to malo brže da ide,

4218
01:46:02,300 --> 01:46:03,440
 ali evo za sad

4219
01:46:03,440 --> 01:46:04,860
 bar pokušamo,

4220
01:46:04,860 --> 01:46:06,100
 imamo početne te,

4221
01:46:06,100 --> 01:46:08,020
 mislim imamo puno rezultata,

4222
01:46:08,020 --> 01:46:10,580
 ali početne sad recimo

4223
01:46:10,580 --> 01:46:12,260
 već imamo reforme Crna Gora.

4224
01:46:12,260 --> 01:46:14,940
 Oni su odlučili da kreću na NTC.

4225
01:46:14,940 --> 01:46:16,640
 Nema rezultata,

4226
01:46:16,640 --> 01:46:17,860
 slabi su na PSAT-u

4227
01:46:17,860 --> 01:46:19,040
 uz Bosnu, Albaniju,

4228
01:46:19,040 --> 01:46:20,140
 najslabi u Evropi

4229
01:46:20,140 --> 01:46:22,240
 i oni kreću reformu.

4230
01:46:22,240 --> 01:46:23,260
 Već prvo za pola godina

4231
01:46:23,260 --> 01:46:24,620
 ima jako puno rezultata.

4232
01:46:24,620 --> 01:46:26,740
 Tako da ja se nadam

4233
01:46:26,740 --> 01:46:28,240
 da će to malo više da se radi,

4234
01:46:28,240 --> 01:46:30,180
 da pomognemo i deci,

4235
01:46:30,180 --> 01:46:31,880
 a naravno i sebi.

4236
01:46:33,440 --> 01:46:35,600
 Kapućino?

4237
01:46:35,600 --> 01:46:36,340
 Meni isto.

4238
01:46:40,600 --> 01:46:43,020
 Novi okus isti užitak.

4239
01:46:43,020 --> 01:46:47,720
 Viraj okus vrhunske kvalitete.

4240
01:46:47,720 --> 01:46:49,600
 Frank, svaki dan.

4241
01:46:52,600 --> 01:46:54,160
 želim vam svu sreću

4242
01:46:54,160 --> 01:46:56,320
 u vašem radu

4243
01:46:56,320 --> 01:46:57,600
 i da vam

4244
01:46:57,600 --> 01:46:58,880
 najbitnije rješenja

4245
01:46:58,880 --> 01:46:59,620
 dođu kroz san.

4246
01:46:59,620 --> 01:47:01,180
 Hvala.

4247
01:47:01,180 --> 01:47:02,740
 Baš mi je bio gušten.

4248
01:47:02,740 --> 01:47:03,520
 Hvala vam puno.

4249
01:47:03,520 --> 01:47:03,840
 Super.

4250
01:47:03,840 --> 01:47:06,780
 Vidimo se ljudi

4251
01:47:06,780 --> 01:47:07,980
 za tjedan dana.

4252
01:47:07,980 --> 01:47:08,460
 Boga.

4253
01:47:08,460 --> 01:47:11,080
 Boš jako dobro.

